0made%20it%20through%20the%20worst%20that%20you%20can%20do.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lee%20Korty%20and%20Bert%20Morton%20holding%20each%20other%20with%20eyes%20closed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cbd0da6fcb546d2d4f5e4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJess%20T.%20Dugan%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Share%20the%20same%20core%20values%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EActivism%20plays%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20Morton%20and%20Korty%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20happiness.%20After%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffauci-ptsd-aids-epidemic-cries-documentary-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EHIV%2FAIDS%20crisis%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9880s%2C%20the%20couple%20felt%20like%20there%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20much%20visibility%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flgbtq%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELGBTQ%2B%20community%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20they%20lived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20not%20seen%20a%20whole%20lot%20of%20active%20community%20other%20than%20at%20the%20bars%2C%E2%80%9D%20Morton%20said.%20%E2%80%9CLots%20of%20people%20continued%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20closet%2C%20but%20we%20just%20decided%20that%20we%20needed%20to%20be%20visible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20are%20involved%20in%20local%20LGBTQ%2B%20groups%20like%20the%20Coalition%20of%20Rainbow%20Alliances%20(CORAL).%20Korty%20offers%20free%20tax%20filing%20services%2C%20while%20Morton%20works%20in%20community-building%20and%20event%20coordination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorton%20said%20working%20together%20and%20seeing%20so%20much%20progress%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flgbtq-survivor-benefits-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ELGBTQ%2