%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20first%20met%20in%20%E2%80%94%20you%20probably%20guessed%20it%20%E2%80%94%20a%20psychology%20class%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Michigan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20junior%20and%20Bev%20was%20a%20sophomore%2C%20and%20we%20began%20dating%20that%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20Richard%2C%2079%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20After%20graduating%2C%20Richard%20went%20to%20medical%20school%20at%20Ohio%20State%20while%20Beverly%20worked%20on%20her%20Ph.D.%20from%20the%20same%20institution%2C%20and%20eventually%20ended%20up%20in%20southern%20California%2C%20where%20they%E2%80%99ve%20stayed%20ever%20since.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Palmers%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epartly%20credit%20their%20marital%20success%20to%20both%20being%20in%20fields%20that%20promote%20listening%20and%20flexible%20thinking.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20we%20met%20in%20a%20psychology%20course%20and%20we%20read%20each%20other's%20textbooks%20a%20lot%20along%20the%20way%2C%20we%20had%20very%20similar%20backgrounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20Beverly%2C%2078%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dd693a1b7293e2a5e011b9e722b742c42ab1062d57601b7ea7b0d812ea908518f%26postID%3D65ca3e21a1efc84fa4427e9f%26postSlug%3Dhow-to-stop-having-the-same-couples-fight-over-and-over-2024-2%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FLove-Demystified-Strategies-Successful-Life%252Fdp%252F0999772023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewho%20wrote%20a%20book%20on%20relationship%20communication%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20said%20he%E2%80%99s%20also%20learned%20from%20his%20own%20clients.%20%E2%80%9CI%20see%20some%20of%20the%20pitfalls%20that%20they%20have%20and%20I%20think%20I've%20learned%20to%20try%20to%20avoid%20them%20in%20my%20own%20marriage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Beverly%20said%20married%20couples%20where%20one%20or%20both%20people%20retire%20can%20really%20struggle%20with%20getting%20along%20when%20their%20careers%20are%20no%20longer%20in%20the%20picture.%20%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20it's%20so%20important%20that%20when%20people%20retire%20that%20they%20move%20on%20to%20something%2C%20not%20just%20stop%20their%20work%2C%20which%20in%20so%20many%20ways%20is%20really%20their%20identity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20why%2C%20despite%20having%20so%20much%20in%20common%2C%20the%20Palmers%20deeply%20prioritize%20their%20independence%20within%20the%20relationship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20how%20they%20communicate%20to%20what%20they%20do%20when%20they%E2%80%99re%20apart%2C%20they%20shared%20their%20best%20tips%20for%20avoiding%20the%20cyclical%20fights%20that%20can%20chisel%20away%20at%20even%20the%20happiest%20marriages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Find%20your%20own%20space%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Older%20couple%20in%20their%20office%20space%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cba6e594aa8ee8e84abacf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EPeyton%20Fulford%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-youre-in-a-healthy-relationship-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esigns%20of%20a%20healthy%20relationship%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20having%20identities%20outside%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20wonderful%20to%20share%20interests%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20Beverly%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20think%20what's%20equally%20important%20is%20each%20of%20the%20partners%20having%20their%20own%20interests%2C%20so%20they%20can%20bring%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20things%20into%20the%20relationship.%E2%80%9D%20Doing%20so%20can%20add%20liveliness%20to%20the%20relationship%20that%20can%20reduce%20conflict%20in%20general%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20have%20healthy%20separ