E%3Cp%3EHD%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhdsa.org%2Fwhat-is-hd%2Foverview-of-huntingtons-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erare%20hereditary%20condition%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20causes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresearchers-use-crispr-to-edit-dna-of-huntingtons-disease-patients-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enerve%20cells%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20brain%20to%20decay%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20eventually%20die.%20It%20also%20causes%20your%20body%20to%20break%20down%2C%20resulting%20in%20symptoms%20like%20random%20body%20movements%2C%20changes%20in%20behavior%20and%20personality%2C%20and%20problems%20walking%20and%20talking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESymptoms%20typically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fhuntingtons-disease-life-expectancy%23life-expectancy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estart%20%3C%2Fa%3Earound%20age%2045%2C%20and%20onset%20can%20be%20quick%2C%20with%20many%20patients%20confined%20to%20a%20wheelchair%20and%20needing%20full-time%20care%20within%20a%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatients%20at%20risk%20%E2%80%94%20only%20about%20200%2C000%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20have%20a%2050%25%20chance%20of%20inheriting%20the%20mutated%20gene%20that%20causes%20HD.%20Those%20aren't%20great%20odds%2C%20considering%20how%20the%20disease%20progresses%2C%20and%20death%20is%20certain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20HD%20is%20a%20lesser-known%20condition%2C%20some%20may%20remember%20it%20from%20Olivia%20Wilde's%20character%2C%20Remy%20%26quot%3BThirteen%26quot%3B%20Hadley%2C%20on%20the%20TV%20show%20%26quot%3BHouse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20show%20focused%20on%20the%20emotional%20toll%20of%20HD%2C%20dedicating%20episodes%20to%20chronicling%20Thirteen's%20journey%20of%20anger%20and%20reckless%20behavior%20before%20coming%20to%20terms%20with%20her%20fate%20and%20eventually%20getting%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%20I%20have%20a%20similar%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20was%20a%20teenager%20when%20I%20learned%20about%20the%20risk%20of%20Huntington's%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20adopted%20at%2014%20months%20old%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20aware%20of%20most%20of%20the%20details%20of%20my%20adoption%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20remember.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20of%20my%20birth%20mother%20holding%20me%20as%20a%20newborn%2C%20taken%20on%20July%204%2C%201995%2C%20in%20central%20Florida.%20I%20was%2011%20days%20old.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca44b3610ab33aa5df0c1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20of%20my%20birth%20mother%20holding%20me%20as%20a%20newborn%2C%20taken%20on%20July%204%2C%201995%2C%20in%20central%20Florida.%20I%20was%2011%20days%20old.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20my%20father%20is%20unknown%20(but%20I%20understand%20he's%20Puerto%20Rican)%2C%20I%20knew%20my%20birth%20mother%20was%20named%20Mary%2C%20and%20I%20was%20born%20with%20the%20name%20Desiree%20before%20it%20was%20changed%20to%20Taylor%20after%20adoption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20only%20learned%20about%20Huntington's%20after%20rummaging%20through%20some%20old%20adoption%20papers%20one%20random%20November%20afternoon%20when%20I%20was%2016.%20(I%20also%20discovered%20a%20few%20half-siblings%2C%20but%20that's%20a%20different%20story).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20finding%20the%20medical%20history%20of%20my%20birth%20mother.%20A%20quick%20Google%20search%20later%2C%20I%20was%20crippled%20with%20fear%2C%20and%20my%20head%20filled%20with%20a%20million%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20my%20adopted%20mother%20(who%2C%20to%20be%20clear%2C%20I%20consider%20my%20real%20mother)%20was%20horrified%20at%20the%20way%20I%20found%20out.%20But%20her%20reason%20for%20not%20telling%20me%20was%20understandable%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20blame%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222101%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20mother%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Sagrada%20Familia%20in%20Spain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca3f2c610ab33aa5df0645%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20mom%20adopted%20me%20in%20August%201996.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20living%20with%20a%20social%20worker.%20Pictured%20is%20us%20in%20Spain%20in%20April%202023.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20decision%20mostly%20came%20down%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20HD%20patients%20typically%20have%20to%20be%2018%20years%20of%20age%20or%20older%20to%20get%20tested%2C%20and%20she%20worried%20about%20the%20potential%20emotional%20toll%20a%20positive%20test%20could%20have%20on%20me%20as%20a%20teenager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20fears%20were%20pretty%20on%20the%20nose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20being%20angry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20discovering%20the%20possibility%20of%20having%20the%20disease%2C%20I%20stopped%20being%20the%20straight-A%2C%20goody%20two-shoe%20student%20I%20once%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHD-fueled%20emotions%20soon%20ruined%20the%20big%20junior%20field%20trip%20I%20had%20been%20looking%20forward%20to%20all%20year%2C%20and%20I%20stopped%20caring%20to%20show%20up%20to%20class%20on%20time.%20Guilt%20weighed%20on%20me%2C%20too%2C%20especially%20after%20my%20then-boyfriend%20complained%20about%20me%20being%20%26quot%3Btoo%20sad%26quot%3B%20around%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20strongest%20emotion%20I%20felt%20was%20anger%2C%20though.%20A%20trauma%20like%20the%20prospect%20of%20HD%20puts%20a%20lot%20into%20question%2C%20and%20it%20made%20me%20start%20looking%20at%20things%20like%20mortality%20and%20religion%20very%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20plagued%20with%20the%20burden%20of%20deciding%20whether%20I%20even%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20I%20had%20the%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20getting%20tested%20would%20help%20me%20better%20plan%20my%20future%2C%20but%20I'd%20have%20to%20live%20with%20the%20reality%20if%20the%20diagnosis%20was%20positive.%20You%20can%20imagine%20that%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20not%20getting%20tested%20would%20always%20leave%20an%20ounce%20of%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head.%20And%2C%20this%20choice%20would%20extinguish%20any%20thoughts%20of%20having%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20it%20just%20wouldn't%20be%20worth%20the%20risk%20of%20continuing%20the%20vicious%20hereditary%20cycle%20if%20I%20were%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20birth%20mother%2C%20Mary.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca42bd6fcb546d2d4e85db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20old%20photo%20of%20the%20author's%20birth%20mother%2C%20Mary.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20it%20didn't%20take%20long%20for%20me%20to%20decide.%20I%20had%20an%20epiphany%20after%20my%20history%20teacher%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20few%20teachers%20who%20showed%20me%20any%20sort%20of%20grace%20at%20this%20time%20%E2%80%94%20told%20me%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20give%20myself%20permission%20to%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20such%20simple%20advice%2C%20but%20something%20about%20it%20clicked%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENot%20knowing%20pushed%20my%20life%20into%20hyperdrive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20life%20expectancy%20of%20someone%20living%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhdsa.org%2Fwhat-is-hd%2Foverview-of-huntingtons-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHD%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%2010%20to%2025%20years%20after%20diagnosis%2C%20which%20typically%20happens%20between%2035%20and%2050%20years%20of%20age.%20But%20those%20years%20of%20decline%20aren't%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20thinking%20about%20getting%20tested%2C%20I%20worried%20a%20positive%20result%20would%20send%20me%20spiraling%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20any%20potential%20symptoms%20were%20some%2020-odd%20years%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20wait%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20pledged%20going%20forward%20to%20live%20my%20life%20as%20if%20I%20had%20Huntington's.%20I%20thought%20starting%20to%20accept%20it%20early%20would%20ease%20the%20disappointment%20if%20I%20one%20day%20started%20showing%20symptoms%2C%20and%20the%20strategy%20worked%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20her%20paperwork%2C%20my%20birth%20mom%20started%20showing%20symptoms%20by%20the%20time%20she%20was%2034%20years%20old.%20Granted%2C%20her%20addiction%20problems%20could%20have%20made%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5331869%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDrug%2520abuse%2520seems%2520to%2520have%2Cgroup%2520(effect%2520size%25200.34).%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eonset%20occur%20faster%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%2016-year-old%20logic%20at%20the%20time%20estimated%20I%20had%20until%20at%20least%2050%20with%20a%20positive%20diagnosis%2C%20assuming%20it%20wasn't%20as%20severe%20as%20Wilde's%20character%20in%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20head%2C%20that%20meant%20I%20had%20to%20fit%20some%2060%20years%20of%20life%20into%20just%2030%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20the%20road%20I%20took.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20junior%20year%2C%20my%20slipping%20grades%20soon%20turned%20back%20into%20A's%2C%20I%20got%20accepted%20to%20my%20first%20choice%20college%2C%20and%20I%20went%20to%20my%20junior%20and%20senior%20prom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Traveling%20to%20Antarctica%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca39e6610ab33aa5df025a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20reached%20my%20seventh%20continent%20in%20November%202022.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20got%20a%20degree%20in%20aviation%20in%20less%20than%20four%20years%20from%20Florida%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20and%20landed%20this%20nifty%20reporting%20job%20at%20Business%20Insider%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20a%20few%20side%20adventures%20studying%20abroad%20in%20China%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflying-on-tiny-planes-versus-commercial-airliners-safety-fun-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20in%20Alaska%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20volunteering%20in%20Bulgaria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20even%20managed%20to%20visit%20more%20than%2050%20countries%20across%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fantarctica-i-do-not-regret-visiting-cruise-expensive-review-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eall%20seven%20continents.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20admit%20the%20excessive%20travel%20and%20spontaneous%20adventures%20(which%20had%20me%20working%20three%20jobs%20at%20one%20point%20to%20afford)%20were%20a%20coping%20mechanism%20for%20HD%2C%20but%20at%20least%20I%20channeled%20it%20into%20something%20good%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20finally%20got%20tested%20after%2010%20years%20of%20not%20knowing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20I%20was%20about%2024%2C%20I%20was%20busy%20traveling%20on%20weekends%20and%20going%20to%20pub%20trivia%20every%20Thursday%20with%20friends.%20By%20then%2C%20I%20was%20thinking%20about%20HD%20less%20and%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%202018%2C%20when%20I%20met%20my%20now-husband%2C%20Ryan%2C%20that%20I%20gave%20getting%20tested%20another%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%3F%20He%20wanted%20kids%20but%20knew%20it%20was%20off%20the%20table%20without%20me%20getting%20a%20negative%20HD%20result.%20And%20he%20was%20OK%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20that%20if%20he%20was%20willing%20to%20sacrifice%20becoming%20a%20father%20just%20to%20marry%20me%2C%20then%20I%20would%20find%20the%20courage%20to%20get%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20Connecticut%20(where%20I%20live)%20has%20a%20large%20HD%20clinic%2C%20and%20I%20finally%20got%20tested%20in%20April%202022%20at%2026%20years%20old.%20The%20process%20was%20brutal%2C%20involving%20multiple%20appointments%20and%20psych%20exams%2C%20before%20I%20handed%20over%20a%20blood%20sample%20for%20genetic%20testing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20agonizing%20weeks%20of%20waiting%2C%20the%20coin%20flipped%20in%20my%20favor%20%E2%80%94%20I%20was%20HD%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222796%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Navy%20jet%20at%20the%20aviation%20museum%20in%20Honolulu.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ca3c4e6fcb546d2d4e8093%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222097%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20husband%20is%20an%20airline%20pilot%2C%20so%20we%20couldn't%20skip%20visiting%20the%20Pearl%20Harbor%20Aviation%20Museum%20during%20our%20honeymoon%20last%20year.%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Rains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%2010%20years%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20a%20huge%20weight%20was%20lifted%20from%20my%20shoulders.%20I%20probably%20could%20have%20let%20myself%20off%20the%20hook%20earlier%20from%20that%20weight%20had%20I%20tested%20at%2018%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20regret%20my%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20became%20stronger%20and%20braver%20living%20under%20the%20threat%20of%20HD%2C%20and%20I%20can%20proudly%20say%20I've%20met%20nearly%20every%20life%20milestone%20I%20wanted%20to%20hit%20by%20the%20age%20of%2030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%2C%20I%20have%20the%20option%20of%20starting%20a%20family.%20It's%20a%20freeing%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuntingtons-disease-no-regrets-after-delaying-tes