n%20essay%20on%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20just%20before%20Modi%20became%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20and%20sent%20it%20to%20Advani%20for%20his%20advice%2C%20amongst%20other%20comments%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20comments%20Advani%20made%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CModi%E2%80%99s%20voice%20betrays%20his%20authoritarian%20streak%20more%20straightforwardly%20than%20anything%20else%20that%20he%20does.%20Anyone%20who%20has%20heard%20him%20speak%20in%20public%20instantaneously%20recognizes%20that%20he%20is%20a%20fascist%20of%20thoroughbred%20pedigree%E2%80%A6you%20only%20have%20to%20listen%20to%20Modi%20for%2015%20minutes%20to%20know%20this%20is%20a%20man%20who%20will%20remove%20anyone%20who%20comes%20in%20his%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20engaging%20exchanges%20between%20Advani%20and%20Guha%20is%20over%20Shashi%20Tharoor.%20Tharoor%2C%20like%20them%2C%20is%20also%20an%20ex-Stephanian.%20Advani%20compared%20Tharoor%20%E2%80%9Cunfavourably%20to%20other%20novelists%20from%20St.%20Stephens%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Framachandra-guha-rukun-advani-shashi-tharoor-st-stephens%5C%22%3ERukun%20Advani%2C%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20and%20the%20Necessity%20to%20Impress%20Others%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuha%20said%20Tharoor%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccharming%20and%20outgoing%20but%2C%20from%20the%20start%2C%20ferociously%20ambitious.%20Shashi%20wanted%20to%20make%20a%20mark%20in%20the%20world%2C%20quicker%20and%20more%20dramatically%20than%20any%20Stephanian%20(or%20perhaps%20any%20Indian)%20before%20him%E2%80%9D.%20Indeed%2C%20Advani%20compared%20Shashi%20to%20%E2%80%9CMacbeth%20with%20vaulting%20ambition%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20Guha%20talks%20about%20the%20early%20years%20of%20their%20friendship%20when%20Advani%20and%20he%20would%20meet%20for%20lunch%20at%20Kwality%E2%80%99s%20in%20Connaught%20Place%20and%20go%20for%20long%20walks%20in%20Lodi%20Garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2010-15%20years%2C%20Advani%20effectively%20cut%20himself%20off%20from%20the%20world%20and%20retreated%20to%20Ranikhet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20their%20last%20meeting%20in%20March-April%202019%2C%20Guha%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20seen%20him%20long%20enough%20to%20sense%20that%20he%20was%20happy%20in%20his%20reclusiveness.%20To%20mail%20him%20sometimes%2C%20to%20think%20of%20him%20often%2C%20made%20me%20happy%20too.%20But%20to%20demand%20to%20speak%20to%20him%20more%20%E2%80%93%20on%20the%20phone%20or%20in%20the%20flesh%20%E2%80%93%20would%20be%20an%20intrusion.%20Things%20were%20best%20left%20as%20they%20were%20%E2%80%93%20for%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interview%20ends%20with%20Ramachandra%20Guha%20saying%20the%20one%20thing%20he%20hopes%20for%20is%20a%20last%20long%2C%20chatty%20lunch%20with%20Rukun%20Advani.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707908459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14160550%2FKT-14-Feb.00_35_11_15.Still002.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwatch-ramachandra-guha-on-the-man-who-made-him-an-author-rukun-advani%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20Guha%E2%80%99s%20account%2C%20Advani%20emerges%20as%20an%20extremely%20perceptive%20and%20insightful%20observer%20of%20human%20nature%20and%20character.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fwatch-ramachandra-guha-on-the-man-who-made-him-an-author-rukun-advani%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arun%20Dhumal%3A%20'IPL%20most%20likely%20to%20start%20from...'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707908457000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107691597%2Cimgsize-76024.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fipl-most-likely-to-sta