iving%20space%20was%20a%20typical%20single-car%20garage.%20However%2C%20I%20extended%20it%20by%20about%20five%20feet%20to%20create%20one%20long%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20small%20bedroom%20with%20a%20closet%20at%20the%20front%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20living%20and%20dining%20area%2C%20and%20then%20a%20galley%20kitchen.%20It%20also%20has%20a%20bathroom%20with%20a%20shower.%20Outside%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20private%20fenced-in%20patio%20where%20people%20can%20sit%2C%20barbecue%2C%20or%20hang%20out%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20keep%20rent%20pretty%20affordable%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20charge%20my%20tenants%20%241%2C100%20a%20month%20in%20rent%2C%20which%20is%20very%20low%20for%20New%20York.%20It's%20only%20increased%20by%20about%20%24100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20choosing%20tenants%2C%20I%20go%20through%20a%20real-estate%20broker%20who%20screens%20and%20checks%20their%20credit%20reports.%20I%20want%20renters%20that%20are%20reliable%20and%20employed.%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20kicking%20somebody%20out%20if%20they%20haven't%20paid%20rent%20or%20if%20they%20damage%20the%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20really%20one%20rule%20for%20renting%20here%3A%20No%20smoking%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20very%20fortunate%20to%20have%20tenants%20who%20are%2050%20and%20over%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20throw%20parties%20or%20anything.%20They're%20usually%20quiet%20and%20just%20go%20to%20work%20and%20come%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there%20are%20additional%20costs%20that%20come%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvermont-tiny-home-adu-grant-money-boomer-low-income-housing-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehaving%20an%20ADU%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20With%20someone%20else%20using%20water%20and%20electricity%2C%20the%20bills%20are%20higher.%20You%20also%20have%20to%20make%20repairs%2C%20like%20if%20the%20stove%20breaks.%20I've%20also%20had%20to%20purchase%20a%20new%20refrigerator.%20And%20when%20someone%20moves%20out%2C%20you%20have%20to%20repaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20think%20New%20York%E2%80%99s%20new%20ADU%20program%20is%20great%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20living%20has%20continued%20to%20increase%20since%20I%20retired%2020%20years%20ago%2C%20so%20my%20ADU%20has%20been%20a%20blessing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20something%20that%20helps%20me%20with%20costs%2C%20and%20I'm%20also%20providing%20a%20home%20for%20people%20that%20are%20in%20need%20of%20affordable%20housing%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20win-win.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20think%20the%20neighborhood%20benefits%20from%20ADUs%20and%20their%20tenants.%20The%20people%20we%20rent%20to%20are%20hardworking%20and%20contributing%20to%20our%20community.%20They%20are%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222362%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20Long%20Island%2C%20New%20York.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cb95416fcb546d2d4f0f50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221574%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoxwill's%20hometown%20of%20Huntington%20is%20located%20on%20Long%20Island%2C%20pictured%20here%20in%20autumn.%3Cp%3EWisKay%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20New%20York%E2%80%99s%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinance-adu-vermont-pay-homeowner-build-rental-property-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EADU%20incentive%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20great%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20wish%20this%20would%20have%20happened%20a%20lot%20sooner.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20very%20helpful.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20Island's%20population%20has%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%20and%20so%20have%20home%20prices.%20I%20just%20read%20an%20article%20in%20a%20local%20newspaper%20that%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsday.com%2Fbusiness%2Flong-island-homes-for-sale-prices-mortgage-rates-ql0e8jjm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20average%20home%20here%20is%20going%20for%20%24600%2C000%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20aren't%20many%20places%20where%20young%20people%20can%20afford%20to%20live%2C%20and%20many%20older%20people%20have%20had%20to%20move%20to%20other%20states%20due%20to%20high%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20heard%20that%20in%20some%20communities%2C%20people%20are%20asking%2C%20%E2%80%9CHow%20come%20we%20don't%20have%20this%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20this%20here.%E2%80%9D%20If%20there%20had%20been%20programs%20to%20help%20people%20build%20ADUs%20a%20long%20time%20ago%2C%20that%20would%20have%20been%20a%20huge%20benefit%20to%20our%20community%20on%20so%20many%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccessory-dwelling-unit-new-york-adu-pays-mortgage-funds-retirement-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707907381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65cbed8194aa8ee8e84b137d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccessory-dwelling-unit-new-york-adu-pays-mortgage-funds-retirement-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Retired%20educator%20Helen%20Boxwill%20said%20rental%20income%20from%20her%20ADU's%20three%20tenants%20over%2020%20years%20has%20helped%20her%20pay%20property%20taxes%20and%20other%20bills.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22alloyd%40insider.com%20(Alcynna%20Lloyd)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccessory-dwelling-unit-new-york-adu-pays-mortgage-funds-retirement-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Two%20Seoul%20police%20officers%20convicted%20over%20deadly%20Halloween%20crush%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707907225000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107692077%2Cimgsize-37288.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftwo-seoul-police-officers-convicted-over-deadly-halloween-crush%2Farticleshow%2F107691172.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107691172.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20South%20Korean%20court%20sentenced%20two%20former%20senior%20police%20officers%20Wednesday%20for%20destroying%20evidence%20linked%20to%20Seoul's%20deadly%202022%20Halloween%20crush%20--%20the%20first%20police%20officials%20to%20be%20sentenced%20over%20the%20disaster.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20--%20mostly%20in%20their%2020s%20and%2030s%20--%20had%20been%20out%20on%20October%2029%2C%202022%2C%20to%20enjoy%20the%20first%20post-pandemic%20holiday%20celebrations%20in%20the%20popular%20Itaewon%20nightlife%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftwo-seoul-police-officers-convicted-over-deadly-halloween-crush%2Farticleshow%2F107691172.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftwo-seoul-police-officers-convicted-over-deadly-halloween-crush%2Famp_articleshow%2F107691172.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftwo-seoul-police-officers-convicted-over-deadly-halloween-crush%2Famp_articleshow%2F107691172.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengal%20BJP%20Chief%20In%20Hospital%20After%20Clash%20With%20Cops%20On%20Way%20To%20Sandeshkhali%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDramatic%20scenes%20played%20out%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali%20this%20afternoon%20as%20BJP%20workers%20clashed%20with%20cops%20in%20their%20attempt%20to%20visit%20women%20who%20have%20accused%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leaders%20of%20sexual%20abuse.%20State%20BJP%20president%20Sukanta%20Majumdar%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital%20after%20he%20fainted%20and%20suffered%20injuries%20during%20a%20scuffle%20with%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Majumdar%20has%20been%20camping%20in%20the%20area%20after%20Sandeshkali%2C%20an%20area%20in%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20made%20headlines%20owing%20to%20shocking%20allegations%20by%20local%20women%20against%20Trinamool%20strongman%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20aides.%20Shahjahan%20is%20on%20the%20run%20for%20a%20month%20now%20after%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20team%2C%20which%20raided%20his%20home%20in%20a%20ration%20scam%20case%2C%20came%20under%20a%20mob%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20BJP%20chief%20and%20other%20party%20workers%20held%20a%20sit-in%20protest%20outside%20the%20police%20superintendent's%20office%20in%20Basirhat%2C%20demanding%20that%20they%20be%20allowed%20to%20visit%20Sandeshkhali.%20The%20local%20administration%20has%20imposed%20prohibitory%20orders%20in%20the%20area%2C%20flagging%20concerns%20of%20a%20breach%20of%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20morning%2C%20Mr%20Majumdar%20alleged%20that%20he%20had%20been%20put%20under%20%26quot%3Bhouse%20arrest%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BI%20decided%20to%20stay%20at%20a%20lodge%20in%20Taki%20so%20that%20I%20could%20easily%20visit%20Sandeshkhali.%20But%20this%20morning%2C%20police%20blocked%20the%20entrance%20of%20the%20lodge%20and%20are%20not%20allowing%20me%20to%20step%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20PTI%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20TMC%20workers%20have%20been%20raping%20women%20for%20months%20now%20-%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20Shibu%20Hajra%20and%20Uttam%20Sardar%20are%20raping%20them.%20We%20had%20come%20to%20the%20SP%20peacefully%20with%20the%20demand%20to%20arrest%20them.%20If%20they%20do%20not%20arrest%20them%2C%20how%20will%20the%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20gain%20confidence%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Majumdar%20said%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20had%20accused%20the%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20government%20of%20shielding%20the%20local%20strongman.%20%26quot%3BYou%20(Ms%20Banerjee)%20have%20traded%20the%20dignity%20of%20SC%2FST%2C%20fishermen%20families%20and%20the%20farming%20communities%20and%20their%20women%20for%20your%20political%20benefit%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Trinamool%20has%20trashed%20the%20allegations%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20instigating%20violence.%20Party%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20allegations%20are%20baseless.%20The%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20vitiate%20the%20atmosphere%20of%20the%20area.%20They%20want%20to%20disturb%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20pointed%20to%20visuals%20of%20stone-pelting%20in%20the%20area%20and%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Irani's%20%26quot%3Bprovocative%20comments%26quot%3B%20prompted%20BJP%20workers%20to%20target%20the%20cops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20well-planned%20conspiracy%20by%20the%20BJP%20to%20create%20unrest%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20Yesterday%2C%20Smriti%20Irani%20made%20provocative%20comments%20in%20her%20press%20release%20from%20Delhi%20and%20today%2C%20on%20her%20instructions%2C%20Sukanta%20Majumdar-led%20workers%20and%20supporters%20of%20the%20BJP%20pelted%20stones%20at%20the%20police%20personnel%2C%26quot%3B%20minister%20Shashi%20Panja%20said%20in%20a%20video%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20allegations%20that%20have%20shocked%20the%20country%2C%20a%20group%20of%20women%20from%20Sandeshkhali%20have%20alleged%20that%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20and%20his%20aides%20sexually%20harass%20them%20and%20repeatedly%20ask%20them%20to%20visit%20the%20party%20office.%20%C2%A0There%20are%20also%20allegations%20of%20land%20grab%20by%20local%20Trinamool%20leaders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20uneasy%20calm%20in%20Sandeshkhali.%20