Cem%3Enot%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20smart%2C%20maybe%20even%20criminal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E4.%20Pop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20time%2C%20it%20seemed%20like%20the%20housing%20market%20was%20doing%20a%20speedrun%20through%20Simonsen%E2%80%99s%20checklist.%20There%20were%20the%20runaway%20prices%3A%20Before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20you%20could%20buy%20a%20median-price%20home%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20for%20about%20%24281%2C300%2C%20according%20to%20Redfin.%20Good%20luck%20finding%20that%20kind%20of%20deal%20now%20%E2%80%94%20even%20with%20a%20dip%20from%20pandemic%20highs%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20typical%20house%20there%20has%20swelled%20to%20%24422%2C000%2C%20an%20eye-watering%2050%25%20increase.%20Similar%20stories%20have%20played%20out%20in%20Miami%20(70%25)%2C%20Boise%2C%20Idaho%20(40%25)%2C%20and%20Dallas%20(36%25).%20The%20typical%20household%20would%20have%20to%20spend%20nearly%2034%25%20of%20its%20income%20to%20afford%20major%20homeownership%20expenses%20such%20as%20mortgage%20payments%20and%20property%20taxes%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data%20firm%20Attom%2C%20the%20highest%20percentage%20since%202007%20and%20well%20beyond%20the%2028%25%20debt-to-income%20ratio%20that%E2%80%99s%20typically%20preferred%20by%20lenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20were%20the%20people%20getting%20rich.%20Speculators%20were%20using%20supercheap%20loans%20to%20buy%20homes%2C%20expecting%20to%20profit%20by%20selling%20to%20an%20even%20bigger%20fool%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-flipping-financial-crisis-housing-price-crash-record-bubble-structural-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehome%20flippers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20aspiring%20megalandlords%2C%20and%20Airbnb%20owners%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-advice-tiktok-misleading-financial-advisors-say-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eflaunted%20their%20debt-funded%20miniempires%20on%20TikTok%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20seemingly%20everyone%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agents-realtors-reckoning-housing-market-home-sales-slow-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esigning%20up%20to%20be%20a%20real-estate%20agent%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20usually%20buttoned-up%20real-estate%20professionals%20were%20giving%20off%20bubble%20vibes%3A%20High-flying%20mortgage%20companies%20threw%20lavish%20parties%20featuring%20bands%20such%20as%20Imagine%20Dragons%2C%20while%20Zillow%2C%20the%20ubiquitous%20home-search%20site%2C%20morphed%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimeline-of-how-zillow-stopped-buying-homes-over-two-weeks-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eone%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20homebuyers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20its%20acquisition%20math%20didn%E2%80%99t%20add%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20signs%20seemed%20to%20point%20to%20a%20bubble%2C%20and%20there%20were%20plenty%20of%20people%20predicting%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpop%E2%80%9D%20was%20coming%3A%20In%20late%202022%2C%20the%20prominent%20Wall%20Street%20economist%20Ian%20Shepherdson%20forecast%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fhouse-price-fall-drop-2023-mortgages%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehome%20prices%20to%20fall%20by%20as%20much%20as%2020%25%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20following%20year.%20Goldman%20Sachs%20expected%20a%20more%20modest%2C%20but%20still%20significant%2C%20decline%20of%20up%20to%2010%25%20from%20the%20peak.%20Countless%20headlines%20wondered%20whether%20home%20values%20were%20set%20to%20crash.%20Even%20Federal%20Reserve%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell%2C%20whose%20every%20word%20threatens%20to%20move%20markets%2C%20said%20at%20a%20Brookings%20Institution%20event%20in%202022%20that%20housing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFortuneMagazine%2Fstatus%2F1598407723003117591%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewas%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbubble%E2%80%9D%20during%20the%20pandemic%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20%E2%80%9Cprices%20going%20up%20at%20very%20unsustainable%20levels.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gloomy%20oracles%20could%20even%20point%20to%20an%20instigator%20of%20the%20coming%20collapse.%20The%20Fed%2C%20led%20by%20Powell%2C%20began%20raising%20interest%20rates%20in%20spring%202022%20to%20fight%20inflation%2C%20sending%20mortgage%20rates%20shooting%20upward.%20Mortgage%20rates%20kept%20rising%20through%20most%20of%202023%2C%20eventually%20reaching%20a%2020-year%20high%20in%20October%20of%20nearly%208%25%2C%20up%20from%20less%20than%203%25%20during%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20pandemic%20in%202020%20and%202021.%20Suddenly%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20so%20cheap%20to%20borrow%20money%2C%20making%20it%20tougher%20for%20reckless%20investors%20to%20enter%20the%20market.%20Speculation%20is%20the%20oxygen%20for%20a%20market-frenzy%20fire%2C%20Rick%20Palacios%20Jr.%2C%20the%20director%20of%20research%20and%20managing%20principal%20at%20John%20Burns%20Research%20and%20Consulting%2C%20told%20me.%20By%20hiking%20rates%2C%20the%20Fed%20cut%20off%20the%20air%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20was%20no%20pop%2C%20no%20sudden%20collapse%20in%20home%20prices.%20Even%20with%20mortgage%20rates%20tripling%20and%20buyers%20retreating%2C%20values%20held%20up.%20To%20understand%20why%2C%20you%20have%20to%20look%20at%20the%20fundamentals%20%E2%80%94%20the%20deep-seated%20reasons%20all%20the%20%E2%80%9CBubble%20Boys%2C%E2%80%9D%20doomsayers%2C%20and%20fear-mongering%20headlines%20are%20dead%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EDebunking%20the%20bubble%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERising%20prices%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20steep%2C%20aren%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20constitute%20a%20bubble.%20Prices%20also%20need%20to%20diverge%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Efundamentals%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20the%20basic%20components%20of%20supply%20and%20demand%2C%20that%20determine%20how%20much%20things%20cost.%20If%20the%20run-up%20in%20prices%20defies%20logical%20explanation%20or%20obscures%20sketchy%20business%20practices%2C%20watch%20out.%20In%20the%20years%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20lenders%20came%20up%20with%20creative%20ways%20to%20boost%20demand%3A%20They%20devised%20predatory%20mortgages%20that%20left%20borrowers%20on%20the%20hook%20for%20impossibly%20high%20payments%20once%20their%20teaser%20rates%20expired%20and%20handed%20out%20so-called%20NINJA%20loans%20(no%20income%2C%20no%20job%2C%20and%20no%20assets).%20If%20you%20owned%20a%20home%20at%20that%20time%2C%20you%20might%E2%80%99ve%20felt%20like%20the%20only%20direction%20its%20value%20could%20go%20was%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20housing-bubble%20theory%20was%20always%20going%20to%20age%20poorly%20because%20of%20one%20fact%3A%20The%20pandemic%20soaring%20prices%20were%20justified.%20Prices%20didn%E2%80%99t%20spiral%20out%20of%20control%20because%20we%20built%20too%20many%20homes%20or%20made%20it%20too%20easy%20to%20borrow%20money%2C%20like%20in%202008%3B%20they%20took%20off%20because%20there%20simply%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%20homes%20for%20all%20the%20creditworthy%20people%20who%20wanted%20to%20buy%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20home%20prices%20to%20suddenly%20crash%2C%20there%20would%20have%20to%20be%20a%20pool%20of%20desperate%20sellers%20looking%20to%20offload%20their%20homes%20on%20the%20cheap%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20worse%2C%20losing%20them%20to%20the%20foreclosure%20process.%20Sure%2C%20speculators%20were%20loud%20and%20proud%20about%20their%20get-rich-quick%20schemes%2C%20but%20they%20were%20a%20vocal%20minority.%20And%20regular%20homeowners%20have%20%E2%80%9Cnever%20looked%20this%20good%E2%80%9D%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20their%20financial%20and%20credit%20health%2C%20Logan%20Mohtashami%2C%20the%20lead%20analyst%20at%20HousingWire%20and%20an%20outspoken%20critic%20of%20bubble%20alarmists%2C%20told%20me.%20Less%20than%204%25%20of%20outstanding%20mortgages%20were%20delinquent%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20third%20quarter%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mba.org%2Fnews-and-research%2Fnewsroom%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2F09%2Fmortgage-delinquencies-increase-in-the-third-quarter-of-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMortgage%20Bankers%20Association%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20near-record%20low.%20In%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202023%2C%20the%20median%20credit%20score%20for%20people%20getting%20a%20new%20mortgage%20was%20a%20stellar%20770%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20New%20York.%20(Lenders%20typically%20consider%20a%20score%20above%20700%20to%20be%20a%20marker%20of%20future%20success%20for%20a%20borrower.)%20Almost%2079%25%20of%20homeowners%20with%20a%20mortgage%20have%20locked%20in%20a%20rate%20below%205%25%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.redfin.com%2Fnews-events%2Fpress-releases%2Fdetail%2F1030%2Fredfin-report-89-of-people-with-mortgages-have-an%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBelow%25205%2525%253A%252078.7%2525%2520have%2Cthe%2520first%2520quarter%2520of%25202022.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERedfin%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20analysis%20of%20data%20from%20the%20Federal%20Housing%20Finance%20Agency%20found.%20In%20the%20history%20of%20rates%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20pretty%20incredible%20deal.%20And%20nearly%2040%25%20of%20homeowners%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20to%20stress%20about%20mortgage%20payments%20at%20all%2C%20according%20to%20census%20data%20%E2%80%94%20they%20own%20their%20homes%20free%20and%20clear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20facing%20a%20housing%20bubble%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20staring%20down%20an%20entirely%20different%20crisis%3A%20a%20supply%20shortage%20that%20has%20regular%20buyers%20fighting%20just%20to%20break%20into%20the%20market.%20US%20homebuilders%20spent%20the%20decade%20after%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis%20building%20at%20about%20half%20the%20rate%20of%20the%20three%20decades%20prior%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20housing%20crunch.%20Various%20estimates%20have%20pegged%20the%20national%20housing%20shortage%20anywhere%20between%202%20million%20and%206%20million%20homes.%20The%20supply%20constraint%20hit%20right%20as%20millennials%2C%20the%20largest%20living%20generation%20in%20the%20US%2C%20reached%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-house-home-real-estate-mortgage-rates-rent-debt-boomers-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etheir%20prime%20homebuying%20years%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Add%20in%20people%E2%80%99s%20sudden%20desire%20for%20a%20bigger%20house%20or%20a%20place%20of%20their%20own%20in%20the%20heat%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20and%20the%20recent%20surge%20in%20home%20prices%20seems%20less%20bubbly%20and%20more%20logical.%20The%20lack%20of%20inventory%20is%20the%20reason%20prices%20didn%E2%80%99t%20suddenly%20drop%2C%20even%20when%20mortgage%20rates%20shot%20up.%20Sure%2C%20buyers%20pulled%20back.%20But%20sellers%20pulled%20back%20even%20more%2C%20leaving%20the%20supply-demand%20imbalance%20in%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20savagely%20unhealthy%20housing%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mohtashami%20told%20me.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20market%20that%20just%20had%20too%20many%20people%20chasing%20too%20few%20homes.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStaying%20high%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20tempting%20to%20look%20for%20echoes%20of%202008%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20housing%20market.%20You%20might%20even%20be%20inclined%20to%20cheer%20on%20a%20crash%20in%20prices%20%E2%80%94%20all%20the%20better%20for%20everyone%20who%20feels%20locked%20out%20of%20homeownership.%20But%20cycles%20rarely%20repeat%20in%20the%20same%20way%2C%20Selma%20Hepp%2C%20the%20chief%20economist%20at%20CoreLogic%2C%20told%20me.%20Anything%20that%20could%20incite%20a%20housing%20crash%20probably%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20leave%20average%20consumers%20in%20a%20position%20to%20suddenly%20pounce%20on%20all%20that%20excess%20inventory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFannie%20Mae%20now%20projects%20a%20modest%203.2%25%20increase%20in%20home%20prices%20this%20year%20and%20a%20jump%20in%20home%20sales%2C%20along%20with%20a%20decline%20in%20mortgage%20rates.%20Goldman%20Sachs%20predicts%20a%205%25%20rise%20in%20home%20prices.%20John%20Burns%20Research%20and%20Consulting%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20publish%20an%20exact%20forecast%20of%20home%20prices%2C%20but%20Palacios%20told%20me%20the%20firm%20expected%20to%20see%20a%20similar%20increase%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9Clow%20single%20digits.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20biggest%20threat%20to%20the%20housing%20market%20at%20large%20is%20a%20severe%20economic%20slowdown%2C%20one%20in%20which%20many%20people%20lose%20their%20jobs%20and%20can%E2%80%99t%20pay%20their%20mortgages.%20It%E2%80%99s%20notoriously%20difficult%20to%20estimate%20where%20the%20economy%20is%20headed%2C%20but%20right%20now%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20roaring%20along%2C%20especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feconomy-us-gdp-inflation-federal-reserve-economic-growth-canada-germany-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecompared%20with%20other%20rich%20countries%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Things%20aren%E2%80%99t%20perfect%2C%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsumer-confidence-economy-stock-market-gas-prices-eggs-vibes-recession-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Evibes%20are%20definitely%20up%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20even%20if%20the%20economy%20does%20take%20a%20turn%2C%20a%20run-of-the-mill%20recession%20probably%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20enough%20to%20topple%20the%20housing%20market.%20Things%20would%20have%20to%20get%20so%20bad%20that%20banks%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20the%20mortgage-lending%20space%20almost%20entirely%2C%20as%20they%20did%20during%20the%20foreclosure%20crisis.%20If%20the%20market%20is%20cratering%20and%20nobody%20can%20get%20a%20mortgage%20to%20put%20a%20floor%20on%20prices%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthat%E2%80%99s%20where%20you%20get%20pretty%20meaningful%20declines%20in%20asset%20prices%2C%E2%80%9D%20Palacios%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20silver%20lining%20baked%20into%20all%20this%3A%20Prices%20aren%E2%80%99t%20poised%20to%20drop%2C%20but%20the%20days%20of%20skyrocketing%20valuations%20appear%20to%20be%20behind%20us%2C%20Mohtashami%20told%20me.%20The%20housing%20market%20is%20far%20from%20balanced%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99re%20at%20least%20heading%20in%20that%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20the%20lingering%20fears%20of%20a%20sudden%20fallout%20are%20just%20a%20distraction%20from%20the%20bigger%20issues%20at%20hand.%20The%20bubble%20debate%20was%20fun%3B%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20put%20it%20to%20bed.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fjames-rodriguez%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EJames%20Rodriguez%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20reporter%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20Discourse%20team.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-bubble-home-prices-stay-high-crash-real-estate-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707906361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c64b78917a1dae0244fcc4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-bubble-home-prices-stay-high-crash-real-estate-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you've%20been%20waiting%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20even%20cheering%20%E2%80%94%20for%20the%20housing%20bubble%20to%20pop%20and%20home%20prices%20to%20plummet%2C%20you're%20out%20of%20luck.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jrodriguez%40insider.com%20(James%20Rodriguez)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-bubble-home-prices-stay-high-crash-real-estate-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Exams%202024%20Notification%20Out%2C%20Registration%20Begins%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(UPSC)%20has%20issued%20%C2%A0notification%20for%20Civil%20Services%20Examinations%202024%20and%20commenced%20the%20application%20process.%20Those%20who%20meet%20the%20eligibility%20requirements%20and%20are%20interested%20can%20apply%20online%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fupsconline.nic.in%5C%22%3Eofficial%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20deadline%20for%C2%A0application%20submission%20is%20March%205.%20The%20number%20of%20vacancies%20to%20be%20filled%20through%20the%20examination%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20approximately%201%2C056.%20Preliminary%20examination%20will%20be%20held%20on%20May%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAge%20Limits%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECandidates%20age%20should%20be%20between%2021%20and%2032%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducational%20Qualifications%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECandidates%20are%20required%20to%20possess%20at%20least%20a%20Bachelor's%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20attempts%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECandidates%20are%20allowed%20a%20maximum%20of%20six%20attempts%20for%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE).%20However%2C%20candidates%20from%20the%20SC%2FST%2FOBC%20and%20PwBD%20categories%2C%20who%20are%20otherwise%20eligible%2C%20may%20receive%20relaxation%20in%20the%20number%20of%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPSC%20CSE%202024%20examination%20will%20consist%20of%20three%20stages%3A%20prelims%2C%20mains%2C%20and%20interview.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EPreliminary%20and%20Main%20examination%20scheme%20and%20subjects%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPreliminary%20Exam%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comprises%20two%20compulsory%20papers%2C%20each%20carrying%20200%20marks.%20Both%20papers%20are%20of%20the%20objective%20type%20(multiple-choice%20questions)%20and%20are%20two%20hours%20each.%20General%20Studies%20Paper-II%20is%20a%20qualifying%20paper%20with%20a%20fixed%20minimum%20qualifying%20mark%20of%2033%25.%20The%20question%20papers%20are%20set%20in%20both%20Hindi%20and%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMain%20Examination%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20written%20examination%20includes%20qualifying%20papers%20and%20those%20counted%20for%20merit.%20Qualifying%20papers%20are%20Paper-A%20(Indian%20Language)%20and%20Paper-B%20(English)%2C%20both%20carrying%20300%20marks%20each.%20Papers%20counted%20for%20merit%20cover%20Essay%2C%20General%20Studies-I%2C%20General%20Studies-II%2C%20General%20Studies-III%2C%20General%20Studies-IV%2C%20and%20an%20Optional%20Subject%20(Paper-I)%2C%20each%20carrying%20250%20marks.%20The%20Interview%2FPersonality%20Test%20is%20worth%20275%20marks%2C%20with%20no%20minimum%20qualifying%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWritten%20Test%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20written%20test%20comprises%20nine%20papers%20of%20conventional%20essay%20type%20in%20subjects%20specified%20in%20sub-section%20(B)%20of%20Section-II%2C%20with%20two%20papers%20being%20qualifying%20in%20nature.%20Marks%20from%20compulsory%20papers%20(Paper-I%20to%20Paper-VII)%20and%20the%20interview%2Fpersonality%20test%20contribute%20to%20the%20ranking.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECandidates%20meeting%20the%20minimum%20qualifying%20marks%20in%20the%20written%20part%20will%20be%20called%20for%20an%20interview%2Fpersonality%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECheck%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fupsc.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FNotif-CSP-24-engl-140224.pdf%5C%22%3Edetailed%20notification%3C%2Fa%3E%20here%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707906300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-11%2Fq846j1bs_upsc_625x300_15_November_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fupsc-civil-services-examinations-2024-notification-out-registration-begins-5056032%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Examinations%202024%3A%20The%20deadline%20for%20application%20submission%20is%20March%205.%20The%20number%20of%20vacancies%20to%20be%20filled%20through%20the%20examination%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20approximately%201%2C056.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fupsc-civil-services-examinations-2024-notification-out-registration-begins-5056032%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fupsc-civil-services-examinations-2024-notification-out-registration-begins-5056032%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fupsc-civil-services-examinations-2024-notification-out-registration-begins-5056032%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fans%20mock%20Messi%20over%20Falklands%20and%20call%20him%20'thief'%20after%20Hong%20Kong%20no-show%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707906300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-lionel-messi-inter-miami_6448351.jpg%3F20240208102258%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffans-mock-lionel-messi-over-falklands-and-call-him-thief-after-hong-kong-no-show-13071377%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinese%20football%20fans%20have%20called%20Lionel%20Messi%20a%20%26quot%3Bthief%26quot%3B%20and%20mocked%20him%20over%20the%20Falkland%20Islands.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffans-mock-lionel-messi-over-falklands-and-call-him-thief-after-hong-kong-no-show-13071377%22%2C%22cdn