County%2C%20and%20had%20worked%20for%20decades%20in%20suburban%20Atlanta%20as%20a%20lawyer%20and%20judge%20handling%20mostly%20low-level%20criminal%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20being%20hired%20as%20a%20special%20prosecutor%20by%20Willis%2C%20though%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopencheckbook.fultoncountyga.gov%2F%23!%2Fyear%2FAll%2520Years%2Fexplore%2F0-%2Fvendor_legal_name%2FLaw%2BOffices%2Bof%2BNathan%2BJ.%2BWade%2F1%2Fdepartment_name%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWade%20has%20made%20at%20least%20%24653%2C880%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20the%20District%20Attorney's%20office%20for%20his%20work%20overseeing%20one%20of%20the%20most%20high-profile%20criminal%20corruption%20trials%20in%20US%20history%20%E2%80%94%20and%20in%20both%20of%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20historic%20and%20damning%20allegations%20against%20the%20former%20US%20president%20and%20his%20remaining%20codefendants%20have%20been%2C%20at%20least%20temporarily%2C%20upstaged%20by%20salacious%20accusations%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffulton-county-district-attorney-fanis-willis-nathan-wade-donald-trump-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWillis%20and%20Wade%20had%20been%20entangled%20in%20an%20illicit%20extramarital%20affair%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20somehow%20compromises%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWade%20had%20filed%20for%20divorce%20from%20his%20wife%20on%20Nov.%202%2C%202021%2C%20one%20day%20after%20he%20was%20hired%20by%20Willis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20Mike%20Roman%2C%20a%20former%20Trump%20campaign%20advisor%20and%20codefendant%2C%20filed%20a%20motion%20in%20Fulton%20County%20Superior%20Court%20citing%20Wade's%20divorce%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20it%2C%20they%20allege%20that%20Willis%20benefited%20financially%20from%20hiring%20Wade%20because%20he%20paid%20for%20her%20luxe%20travel%20to%20tropical%20destinations%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Aruba%20and%20Belize%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20warrants%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%20so%20great%20that%20Willis%20and%20her%20office%20should%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20case%2C%20or%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffani-willis-defends-prosecutor-trump-georgia-election-improper-relationship-allegations-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eindictment%20to%20be%20dismissed%20in%20entirety.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20accusations%20have%20taken%20center%20stage%20in%20Trump's%20criminal%20prosecution%2C%20with%20Roman's%20team%20issuing%20subpoenas%20to%20Wade%2C%20Willis%2C%20and%20half%20a%20dozen%20witnesses%20who%20have%20worked%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20hearing%20on%20Monday%20in%20preparation%20for%20the%20blockbuster%20testimony%20later%20this%20week%2C%20a%20prosecutor%20told%20Judge%20Scott%20McAfee%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D4111%26v%3Dewtzcoo9ics%26embeds_referring_euri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Ftwitter.com%252F%26source_ve_path%3DMjM4NTE%26feature%3Demb_title%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWillis'%20own%20father%2C%20also%20a%20lawyer%2C%20will%20be%20called%20to%20testify%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20her%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20father%2C%20John%20C.%20Floyd%20III%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20say%20that%20he%20had%20lived%20with%20his%20daughter%20at%20the%20time%20Roman's%20attorneys%20have%20said%20she%20%26quot%3Bcohabitated%26quot%3B%20with%20Wade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20center%20of%20Thursday's%20hearing%20will%20be%20whether%20either%20prosecutor%20has%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoman's%20attorneys%20must%20prove%20that%20Willis%20acquired%20a%20personal%20interest%20or%20stake%20in%20the%20defendant's%20conviction%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bactual%20conflict%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20simply%20speculative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fulton%20County%20DA%20Fani%20Willis%3B%20Special%20prosecutor%20Nathan%20Wade.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd42027a3d2714887744c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221081%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFulton%20County%20DA%20Fani%20Willis%3B%20Special%20prosecutor%20Nathan%20Wade.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FJohn%20Bazemore%2C%20File%3B%20Elijah%20Nouvelage%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20AP%2C%20Pool%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWillis'%20lawyers%20responded%20earlier%20this%20to%20the%20allegations%20denying%20that%20she%20ever%20benefited%20financially%20from%20a%20relationship%20with%20Wade.%20Her%20lawyers%20have%20written%20that%20no%20financial%20or%20personal%20conflict%20of%20interest%20justifies%20disqualification%20%E2%80%94%20and%20pointed%20to%20two%20ongoing%20relationships%20between%20defense%20attorneys%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20affidavit%2C%20Wade%20denied%20that%20he%20and%20Willis%20were%20in%20a%20relationship%20at%20the%20time%20he%20was%20appointed%20a%20special%20prosecutor%2C%20noting%20that%20they%20had%20been%20professional%20acquaintances%20when%20he%20was%20hired%2C%20and%20that%20became%20more%20personal%20while%20working%20together%20on%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%202022%2C%20District%20Attorney%20Willis%20and%20I%20developed%20a%20personal%20relationship%20in%20addition%20to%20our%20professional%20association%20and%20friendship%2C%26quot%3B%20Wade%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20stopping%20short%20of%20calling%20their%20relationship%20romantic%20and%20insisting%20it%20began%20after%20he%20split%20with%20his%20ex-wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20any%20alleged%20travel%2C%20he%20said%2C%20they%20mostly%20split%20the%20expenses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWillis'%20office%20and%20Wade%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFani%20Willis%20%2B%20Nathan%20Wade%3A%20Is%20this%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20for%20Willis%