0not%20corrupt%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20world%20is%20embracing%20modernity%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20challenges%20emanating%20since%20the%20last%20century%20are%20on%20a%20continuous%20rise.%20Be%20it%20food%20security%2C%20health%20security%2C%20water%20security%2C%20energy%20security%2C%20education%20or%20building%20an%20inclusive%20society%2C%20every%20government%20is%20bound%20by%20many%20responsibilities%20towards%20its%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20his%20government%20remained%20focused%20on%20women-led%20development.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20strengthening%20social%20and%20financial%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20marks%20his%20seventh%20since%202015.%20During%20this%20two-day%20visit%2C%20he%20is%20expected%20to%20engage%20in%20wide-ranging%20talks%20with%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20UAE%20to%20further%20strengthen%20the%20existing%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20highlights%20of%20the%20visit%20is%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20BAPS%20Mandir%2C%20the%20first%20Hindu%20temple%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20later%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20was%20one%20of%20the%20top%20four%20foreign%20direct%20investors%20in%20India%20during%20the%20fiscal%20year%202022-23.%20Bilateral%20trade%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE%20reached%20an%20impressive%20%2485%20billion%20during%20that%20time%2C%20solidifying%20their%20positions%20as%20crucial%20trading%20partners%20for%20each%20other.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20economic%20collaboration%20has%20been%20further%20facilitated%20by%20agreements%20such%20as%20the%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20(CEPA)%20signed%20in%20February%202022%20and%20the%20Local%20Currency%20Settlement%20(LCS)%20System%20established%20in%20July%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20community%2C%20numbering%20around%203.5%20million%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20forms%20the%20largest%20expatriate%20group%20in%20the%20country.%20Their%20contributions%20to%20the%20socio-economic%20development%20of%20the%20UAE%20have%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20fostering%20strong%20people-to-people%20ties.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707905820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fh5q334ok_modi-in-uae_625x300_14_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworld-today-needs-clean-transparent-tech-savvy-governments-pm-modi-in-uae-5055642%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20addressing%20at%20the%20World%20Government%20Summit%20in%20Dubai%2C%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20clean%20and%20transparent%20governance%20as%20a%20crucial%20factor%20in%20addressing%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20governments%20worldwide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworld-today-needs-clean-transparent-tech-savvy-governments-pm-modi-in-uae-5055642%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworld-today-needs-clean-transparent-tech-savvy-governments-pm-modi-in-uae-5055642%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fworld-today-needs-clean-transparent-tech-savvy-governments-pm-modi-in-uae-5055642%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CIAL%2C%20BPCL%20sign%20pact%20to%20set%20up%20first%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20at%20Cochin%20airport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707905796000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F10%2Ffull%2F1691662186-9218.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcial-b