%20to%201984%2C%20precisely%20the%206%20dreaded%2C%20dark%20days%20between%20October%2031-November%205%2C%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F1984-sikh-massacre-remembrance%5C%22%3ESikhs%20were%20slaughtered%20in%20the%20streets%20of%20New%20Delhi%20(and%20other%20places%20across%20the%20country)%20by%20frenzied%20mobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20retaliation%20to%20the%20assassination%20of%20then%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20The%20home%20minister%20of%20India%20and%20de%20facto%20man-in-charge%20of%20the%20country%20at%20the%20time%20was%20none%20other%20than%20Rao.%20According%20to%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20estimates%2C%20upwards%20of%203350%20people%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.humanrightspulse.com%2Fmastercontentblog%2Fthe-1984-sikh-genocide-36-years-on%5C%22%3Ekilled%20in%20New%20Delhi%20alone%20while%20the%20actual%20tally%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20manifold%20higher.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20government%20of%20the%20day%20virtually%20washed%20its%20hands%20off%20of%20the%20basic%20responsibility%20of%20protecting%20the%20citizens.%20Police%20stood%20by%20as%20mute%20spectators%20as%20unspeakable%20horrors%20were%20committed%20against%20hapless%20Sikhs%20in%20an%20act%20of%20systematic%20genocide%2C%20a%20tool%20that%20has%20since%20been%20used%20by%20rightwing%20mobs%20with%20impunity%20against%20other%20minorities%20in%20similar%20subsequent%20massacres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20could%20a%20learned%2C%20self-proclaimed%20intellectual%20like%20Rao%20let%20such%20a%20pogrom%20play%20out%20under%20his%20watch%20as%20the%20home%20minister%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Findia%2F2020%2F06%2F27%2Fnarasimha-rao-the-intellectual-giant-who-never-stopped-learning.html%5C%22%3EA%20tongue%20that%20eloquently%20spoke%2017%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E%20chose%20to%20remain%20tongue-tied%20while%20fellow%20citizens%20were%20mercilessly%20massacred.%20Some%20of%20his%20ardent%20supporters%20would%20like%20us%20to%20believe%20that%20this%20suave%20gentleman%20was%20a%20mere%20bystander%20at%20the%20time%20but%20another%20non-Gandhi%20family%20Congress%20prime%20minister%2C%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20a%20Sikh%20himself%2C%20that%20completed%20not%20one%20but%20two%20terms%20as%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F1984-anti-sikh-riots-had-pv-narasimha-rao-heeded-ik-gujrals-advice-says-manmohan-singh-2143621%5C%22%3Epublicly%20stated%20that%20Rao%20paid%20no%20heed%20to%20repeated%20requests%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20Army%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20stem%20the%20violence%20that%20will%20forever%20remain%20a%20blot%20in%20independent%20India%E2%80%99s%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrime%20minister%20during%201992%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20event%20pertaining%20to%20his%20legacy%20is%20the%20December%206%2C%201992%20destruction%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20Ayodhya.%20By%20then%2C%20Rao%20was%20firmly%20in%20the%20saddle%20as%20the%20indisputable%20prime%20minister%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20now%20a%20well-recognised%20fact%20that%20he%20did%20nothing%20to%20halt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1039933%2Freportage-this-book-captures-lk-advanis-rath-yatra-and-1992-93-riots-in-mumbai%5C%22%3Ethe%20juggernaut%20of%20L.K.%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20vitriolic%20Rath%20Yatra%20that%20not%20only%20flared%20up%20communal%20tensions%20in%20several%20cities%20across%20the%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20culminated%20in%20the%20physical%20razing%20to%20the%20ground%20of%20a%20500-year%20old%20mosque%2C%20the%20ramifications%20of%20which%20are%20still%20felt%20to%20this%20day%20and%20perhaps%20for%20many%20years%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fblog%2Flalu-yadav-on-why-and-how-he-arrested-lk-advani-on-october-23-1990-1784734%5C%22%3EContemporaries%20such%20as%20Lalu%20Yadav%20threw%20Advani%20behind%20the%20bars%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20flagrantly%20riling%20up%20communal%20tensions%20but%20Union%20government%20under%20Rao%20surreptitiously%20allowed%20him%20to%20stoke%20tensions.%20Memoirs%20written%20by%20multiple%20people%20who%20were%20either%20close%20to%20Rao%20at%20that%20time%20or%20were%20part%20of%20his%20cabinet%20have%20proven%20beyond%20doubt%20that%20he%20intentionally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fnarasimha-rao-performed-puja-during-demolition-of-babri-masjid-book%2Farticleshow%2F14687884.cms%5C%22%3Echose%20the%20path%20of%20inaction%20and%20indifference%20in%20the%20light%20of%20historic%20communal%20polarization%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8V3jQ_9davY%5C%22%3Epointed%20out%20in%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20speech%20this%20past%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20PM%20Rao%20was%20busy%20and%20inaccessible%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Epuja%3C%2Fem%3E%20while%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20being%20demolished%20by%20saffron%20goons.%20No%20wonder%20he%20was%20labeled%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpv-narasimha-rao-mani-shankar-aiyar-book-launch%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cfirst%20BJP%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20by%20his%20party%20colleague%20Mani%20Sankar%20Aiyar%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20singular%20event%20of%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20catapulted%20the%20BJP%20from%20a%20fringe%20party%20to%20eventually%20becoming%20the%20numero-uno%20party%20that%20it%20is%20today%20under%20the%20stewardship%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20who%20owes%20it%20to%20those%201992%20events%20for%20his%20eventual%20rise.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20doubled%20up%20as%20both%20Advani%20and%20Rao%20in%20a%20unitary%20role%20when%20it%20came%20to%20his%20turn%20in%202002%20as%20both%20the%20vitriol-spewing%20%3Cem%3Epracharak%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20the%20Nero-eque%20administrator.%20One%20has%20to%20certainly%20appreciate%20the%20humility%20of%20Modi%20in%20paying%20back%20his%20respects%20in%20kind%20to%20Advani%20and%20Rao%20to%20whom%20he%20owes%20so%20much!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20his%20stewardship%20of%201992%20events%2C%20Rao%20holds%20the%20rare%20distinction%20of%20being%20at%20the%20helm%20during%20both%20of%20the%20heinous%20acts%20of%20violence%20in%20the%20Republic%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%20that%20make%20us%20all%20hang%20our%20heads%20in%20shame%20even%20to%20this%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffor-bharat-ratna-chaudhary-charan-singh-politics-meant-the-art-of-possible%5C%22%3EFor%20%E2%80%98Bharat%20Ratna%E2%80%99%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Politics%20Meant%20the%20Art%20of%20the%20Possible%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Corruption%20got%20institutionalised%E2%80%99%20during%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20regime%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20event%20that%20also%20holds%20historical%20significance%20is%20of%20a%20different%20shade%20but%20also%20blot-worthy%20in%20its%20own%20regard.%20In%20July%201993%2C%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20minority%20government%20barely%20scraped%20through%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20by%20allegedly%20bribing%20MPs%20from%20Jharkand%20Mukthi%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(Ajit)%20leading%20to%20the%20narrowest%20margin%20in%20history%20of%20Indian%20Parliament%20of%2014%20votes.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fmagazine%2Fcover-story%2Fstory%2F20051226-jharkhand-mukti-morcha-bribery-scandal-in-1993-corruption-got-institutionalised-in-india-786386-2005-12-25%5C%22%3EAs%20Fali%20Nariman%20put%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20in%20this%20year%20(1993)%20that%20corruption%20got%20institutionalised%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%20The%20no-confidence%20motion%20itself%20was%20tabled%20alleging%20rampant%20corruption%20in%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20government%20and%20h