rking%20alongside%20the%20San%20Mateo%20County%20Crime%20Lab%20to%20collect%20evidence.%20The%20bodies%20have%20been%20taken%20into%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20San%20Mateo%20County%20Coroner%2C%20who%20is%20working%20to%20positively%20identify%20each%20individual%20and%20notify%20next%20of%20kin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20bears%20an%20eerie%20resemblance%20to%20a%20recent%20case%20where%20a%20wealthy%20Indian-origin%20couple%20and%20their%20teenage%20daughter%20were%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20%245%20million%20mansion%20in%20Massachusetts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20month%2C%20at%20least%20seven%20Indian-origin%20people%20have%20been%20found%20dead%20in%20the%20US.%20US%20envoy%20to%20India%20Eric%20Garcetti%20reassured%20that%20the%20US%20is%20committed%20to%20making%20sure%20it%20remains%20a%20safe%20destination%20for%20Indian%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707902340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fmgn5sqas_indian-family_625x300_14_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-couple-twin-sons-found-dead-at-their-home-in-california-5055481%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian-origin%20family%20from%20Kerala%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20their%20home%20in%20US'%20California%20in%20an%20apparent%20case%20of%20murder-suicide.%20The%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Anand%20Sujith%20Henry%2C%2042%2C%20his%20wife%20Alice%20Priyanka%2C%2040%2C%20and%20their%204-year-old%20twin%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-couple-twin-sons-found-dead-at-their-home-in-california-5055481%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-couple-twin-sons-found-dead-at-their-home-in-california-5055481%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2