topping%20them%20from%20crossing%20over%20to%20Haryana%2C%20the%20Haryana%20police%20fired%20pellets%20at%20and%20used%20drones%20to%20teargas%20protesting%20farmers%20leading%20to%20injuries%20and%20chaos%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20border.%20As%20per%20reports%2C%20over%20100%20farmers%20were%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESocial%20media%20accounts%20withheld%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20accounts%20and%20Facebook%20pages%20of%20prominent%20farmer%20leaders%20like%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20the%20coordinator%20of%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20BKU%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20Mann%2C%20Surjit%20Singh%20Phull%20from%20BKU%20Krantikari%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Harpal%20Sangha%2C%20Ashok%20Danoda%20from%20Haryana%20and%20many%20others%20have%20been%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20also%20banned%20official%20pages%20which%20supported%20the%20movement%20and%20posted%20updates%20on%20it%2C%20like%20%40Tractor2twitr_P%20run%20by%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20and%20Progressive%20Farmers%20Front%2C%20run%20by%20Guramneet%20Singh%20Mangat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBKU%20(SBS)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20farmer%20unions%20which%20was%20leading%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20from%20Ambala%2C%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Gaon%20Sawera%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20page%20run%20by%20independent%20journalist%20Mandeep%20Punia%20has%20been%20withheld%2C%20as%20has%20been%20Mandeep%E2%80%99s%20personal%20page.%20Mandeep%20is%20a%20prominent%20name%20supporting%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20and%20had%20been%20arrested%20in%202020.%20In%20the%20jail%2C%20Mandeep%20took%20notes%20on%20his%20legs%20and%20then%20wrote%20a%20report%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Caravan.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20withholding%20these%20accounts%20has%20been%20largely%20understood%20to%20be%20opaque.%20Guramneet%E2%80%99s%20personal%20X%20account%20is%20still%20up%2C%20as%20is%20Jagjit%20Singh%20Dallewal%E2%80%99s%20X%20account.%20But%20Dallewal%E2%80%99s%20Facebook%20page%20is%20banned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accounts%20received%20a%20message%20from%20X%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CYour%20account%20has%20been%20withheld%20in%20IN%20%5BIndia%5D%20in%20response%20to%20a%20legal%20demand.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20official%20page%20of%20Kisan%20Majdoor%20Morcha%2C%20which%20was%20started%20recently%20ahead%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20protest%2C%20is%20still%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20pertinent%20to%20mention%20here%20that%20earlier%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202020-2021%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20banned%20many%20social%20media%20accounts%20including%20the%20official%20page%20of%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%2C%20which%20largely%20functioned%20as%20the%20digital%20outpost%20of%20the%20SKM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20then%20high%20profile%20supporters%20like%20Punjabi%20singer%20Jazzy%20B%20and%20Khalsa%20Aid%E2%80%99s%20Ravi%20Singh%2C%20along%20with%20independent%20journalist%20Sandeep%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20had%20been%20withheld%20and%20continue%20to%20be%20under%20lock%20and%20key.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccounts%20meant%20to%20debunk%20propaganda%20targeted%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20running%20the%20%40Tractor2Twitr_i%20page%20on%20X%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20withheld%20in%20the%20time%20between%20he%20spoke%20and%20this%20report%20was%20published%20%E2%80%93%20said%20that%20all%20these%20accounts%20were%20withheld%20as%20farmer%20leaders%20were%20sitting%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20union%20ministers%20on%20February%2012.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20an%20assumption%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20Union%20government%20but%20the%20Punjab%20government%20too%20which%20was%20involved%20in%20singling%20out%20farmer%20union%20leaders%E2%80%99%20accounts.%20This%20is%20a%20dangerous%20trend%2C%20as%20those%20accounts%20which%20were%20running%20propaganda%20against%20farmers%20are%20getting%20support%20while%20the%20official%20mouthpieces%20of%20farmers%20meant%20to%20debunk%20the%20propaganda%20and%20misinformation%20are%20being%20targeted%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavjit%20said%20that%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%202024%2C%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cagenda%20is%20to%20silence%20all%20those%20who%20dare%20to%20speak%20against%20or%20question%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20as%20it%20will%20affect%20his%20image.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Meeting%20only%20if%20social%20media%20accounts%20restored%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavjit%20said%20that%20the%20leaders%20had%20decided%20to%20boycott%20further%20meetings%20till%20the%20accounts%20are%20restored.%20%E2%80%9CFarmer%20union%20leaders%20have%20decided%20that%20the%20invitation%20for%20a%20third%20round%20of%20meetings%20will%20be%20accepted%20only%20if%20the%20government%20restarts%20these%20social%20media%20accounts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20leader%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20Mann%20also%20shared%20that%20he%20was%20attending%20the%20farmers%20and%20union%20ministers%E2%80%99%20meeting%20on%20February%2012%20night%2C%20when%20he%20got%20a%20message%20on%20WhatsApp%20that%20his%20X%20account%20had%20been%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20showed%20the%20message%20to%20union%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20but%20he%20feigned%20ignorance%20and%20said%20that%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20this%20action.%20I%20asked%20Piyush%20Goyal%20how%20his%20government%20could%20ask%20us%20to%20believe%20them.%20I%20also%20asked%20Punjab%20NRI%20affairs%20minister%20Kuldeep%20Singh%20Dhaliwal%20who%20was%20representing%20the%20Punjab%20government%20if%20it%20was%20the%20AAP%20government%20who%20was%20getting%20our%20social%20media%20accounts%20blocked%20but%20he%20too%20refused%20to%20answer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamandeep%20said%20that%20this%20is%20a%20clear%20attempt%20to%20exert%20pressure%20on%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20afraid%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20strength%2C%20which%20they%20have%20already%20seen%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202020.%20Let%20them%20try%20whatever%20they%20want%20to%2C%20farmers%20are%20united%20and%20committed%20to%20their%20cause%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20spoke%20to%20Harinder%20Happy%2C%20a%20PhD%20student%20from%20JawaharLal%20Nehru%20University%2C%20Delhi%20who%2C%20among%20others%2C%20was%20running%20the%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%2C%20the%20official%20Twitter%20page%20of%20the%20SKM%20last%20time.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20resorted%20to%20these%20tactics%20last%20time%20too%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20two%20years%20since%20they%20banned%20the%20Kisan%20Ekta%20Morcha%20page%2C%20which%20had%20over%20five%20lakh%20followers.%20Our%20page%20was%20withheld%20when%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20was%20at%20its%20peak.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20considering%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%202024%20and%20the%20mass%20support%20for%20farmers%2C%20they%20withheld%20the%20X%20accounts%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day%20of%20the%20protest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHappy%20highlighted%20how%20%E2%80%9Con%20one%20hand%2C%20BJP%20is%20giving%20Bharat%20Ratna%20to%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20and%20M.S.%20Swaminathan%20and%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20they%20were%20not%20implementing%20their%20findings.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707901810000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14132746%2FUntitled-design-7-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20now%20running%20the%20%40Tractor2Twitr_i%20page%20on%20X%20said%20that%20these%20accounts%20were%20withheld%20as%20farmer%20leaders%20were%20sitting%20at%20a%20meeting%20with%20union%20ministers%20on%20February%2012.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%2C%20A%20Challenge%20To%20Delimitation%2C%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Poll'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%20by%20any%20state%20legislature%2C%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Assembly%20today%20adopted%20two%20resolutions%20--%20one%20against%20the%C2%A0delimitation%20exercise%20after%20a%20fresh%20Census%20and%20the%20other%20against%20the%20Centre's%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20push%20for%20simultaneous%20polls%20to%20Assemblies%20and%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20the%20resolution%20against%20the%20delimitation%20plan%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20said%20states%20like%20Tamil%20Nadu%20that%20effectively%20controlled%20population%20should%20not%20be%20penalised%20and%20the%20one%20that%20failed%20should%20not%20be%20rewarded.%20He%20stressed%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20other%20southern%20states%20stand%20to%20lose%20both%20power%20and%20rights%20if%20a%20delimitation%20exercise%20is%20conducted%20without%20considering%20these%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20pointed%20out%20that%20in%201971%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Bihar%20had%20similar%20populations.%20But%20over%20the%20past%20five%20decades%2C%20he%20said%2C%20Bihar's%20population%20has%20surged%20to%20over%20one-and-a-half%20times%20that%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20%26quot%3BAlready%2C%20with%2039%20MPs%2C%20we%20are%20begging.%20If%20numbers%20drop%2C%20what%20will%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20chief%20then%20opposed%20the%20'One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election'%20plan%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20being%20reviewed%20by%20a%20panel%20led%20by%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind.%20Mr%20Stalin%20said%20the%20plan%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20to%20democratic%20decentralisation%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20impractical%2C%20not%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20Elections%20to%20local%20bodies%2C%20state%20assemblies%20and%20parliament%20are%20being%20held%20at%20different%20times%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20people-centric%20issues%20in%20a%20vast%20and%20diverse%20country%20like%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%2C%20supported%20the%20resolution.%20Leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20Legislature%20Party%2C%20K%20Selvaperunthagai%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lie%20that%20elections%20cost%20a%20lot.%20It's%20less%20than%201%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20country's%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AIADMK%2C%20which%20recently%20snapped%20ties%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20offered%20conditional%20support%20to%20the%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20plan.%20The%20main%20Opposition%20party%20backed%20the%20resolution%20against%20the%20delimitation%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLA%20Vanathi%20Srinivasan%20backed%20the%20resolution%20against%20delimitation%20but%20opposed%20the%20one%20challenging%20the%20'One%20Nation%20One%20Election'%20proposal.%20She%20said%20it's%20a%20poll%20reform%20aimed%20at%20seamless%20implementation%20of%20welfare%20schemes%20that%20are%20hampered%20by%20the%20poll%20code%20ahead%20of%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707901800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fi1j6ar84_mk-stalin-1200_625x300_29_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.