0for%20the%20past%20nine%20years.%20They%20had%20moved%20to%20San%20Mateo%20County%20from%20New%20Jersey%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20year%20after%20they%20purchased%20their%20%242.1%20million%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%2C%20a%20former%20Software%20Engineering%20Manager%20at%20Meta%20and%20Google%2C%20and%20Alice%2C%20a%20senior%20analyst%2C%20were%20both%20IT%20professionals.%20Described%20as%20friendly%2C%20hardworking%2C%20and%20devoted%20parents%20by%20neighbors%20and%20colleagues%2C%20the%20couple%20had%20built%20a%20positive%20reputation%20in%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20Anand%20founded%20his%20own%20artificial%20intelligence%20company%2C%20Logits%2C%20after%20leaving%20his%20position%20at%20Meta%20in%20June%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELogits%2C%20which%20specializes%20in%20providing%20enterprises%20with%20the%20means%20to%20privately%20train%20and%20serve%20Generative%20AI%20models%20for%20specific%20business%20needs%2C%20has%20garnered%20attention%20in%20the%20tech%20industry.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%20company's%20website%20is%20down%2C%20and%20the%20reasons%20behind%20Anand's%20departure%20from%20Meta%20and%20the%20establishment%20of%20Logits%20remain%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple's%20marital%20history%20has%20come%20to%20light%2C%20as%20records%20show%20that%20Anand%20had%20filed%20for%20divorce%20in%20December%202016%2C%20years%20before%20the%20birth%20of%20their%20twins.%20However%2C%20the%20divorce%20did%20not%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20family%20had%20moved%20several%20times%20across%20San%20Francisco%20before%20settling%20in%20the%20home%20where%20the%20tragic%20incident%20occurred.%20Authorities%20disclosed%20that%20they%20had%20responded%20to%20calls%20at%20the%20residence%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20since%20the%20family's%20relocation%2C%20but%20the%20nature%20of%20those%20calls%20has%20not%20been%20revealed.%20No%20s