ted%20%26quot%3Bpersistent%20non-compliances%20and%20continued%20material%20supervisory%20concerns%20in%20the%20bank%26quot%3B%20that%20were%20flagged%20after%20a%20comprehensive%20audit%20of%20its%20systems%20by%20external%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Paytm%20bank%20is%20a%20regulated%20entity%20that%20accepts%20the%20deposits%20from%20users%20who%20can%20then%20use%20the%20app%20to%20make%20transactions%2C%20including%20sending%20and%20receiving%20money%2C%20and%20buying%20goods%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Paytm%20Bank%20Came%20Under%20RBI's%20Radar%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20accounts%20created%20without%20proper%20identification%20were%20one%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20for%20the%20RBI's%20action%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20last%20week.%20These%20accounts%20-%20with%20inadequate%20Know-Your-Customer%2C%20or%20KYC%20-%20conducted%20transactions%20worth%20crores%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20leading%20to%20fears%20of%20potential%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20over%201%2C000%20users%20were%20found%20to%20have%20linked%20the%20same%20Permanent%20Account%20Number%2C%20or%20PAN%2C%20to%20their%20accounts.%20These%20were%20found%20during%20verification%20conducted%20by%20the%20RBI%20and%20external%20auditors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2F1000-accounts-1-pan-money-laundering-how-paytm-payments-bank-came-under-rbi-radar-4990243%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%2C000%20Accounts%2C%201%20PAN%3A%20How%20Paytm%20Bank%20Came%20On%20RBI%20Radar%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPaytm%20Stock%20Nosedives%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20January%2031%2C%20Paytm%20stock%20has%20lost%20over%2060%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20value%2C%20eroding%20an%20estimated%20%242.6%20billion%20of%20shareholders'%20wealth.%20At%201.30%20pm%20it%20was%20trading%209.29%20per%20cent%20down%20