cided%20to%20declare%20Kaji%20Nemu%20(Citrus%20Limon)%20as%20the%20State%20Fruit%20of%20Assam.%20With%20its%20unique%20aroma%20and%20antioxidant%20properties%2C%20Assam%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ndtv.com%2Ffood-drinks%2Fzest-up-your-recipes-interesting-ways-you-can-use-lemon-in-cooking-4044923%5C%22%3Elemon%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20enriched%20our%20local%20cuisines.%20With%20today's%20announcement%2C%20it%20is%20set%20to%20shine%20on%20the%20global%20fruit%20map%2C%20boosting%20self-dependency%20and%20production%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOur%20Government%20has%20decided%20to%20declare%20Kaji%20Nemu%20(Citrus%20Limon)%20as%20the%20State%20Fruit%20of%20Assam.%20With%20its%20unique%20aroma%20%26amp%3B%20antioxidant%20properties%2C%20Assam%20lemon%20has%20enriched%20our%20local%20cuisines.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWith%20today's%20announcement%2C%20it%20is%20set%20to%20shine%20on%20the%20global%20fruit%20map%2C%20boosting%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtATTxzixUf%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FtATTxzixUf%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20(%40himantabiswa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhimantabiswa%2Fstatus%2F1757292227343331613%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2013%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ndtv.com%2Fnews%2Frare-assam-tea-sold-for-record-price-of-rs-1-lakh-per-kg-twitter-reacts-2652231%5C%22%3ERare%20Assam%20Tea%20Sold%20For%20Record%20Price%20Of%20Rs.%201%20Lakh%20Per%20Kg%2C%20Twitter%20Reacts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EImportance%20of%20Kaji%20Nemu%20In%20Assam%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgriculture%20Minister%20Atul%20Bora%20announced%20in%20the%20state%20Assembly%20as%20per%20a%20decision%20of%20the%20Cabinet.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Cabinet%20meeting%20yesterd