E%20who%20teaches%20at%20Tufts%20University%2C%20about%20what%20the%20results%20of%20the%20election%20mean%20and%20what%20could%20happen%20next.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20it%20clear%20who%20will%20govern%20Pakistan%20next%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20as%20they%20stand%20mean%20that%20no%20party%20is%20in%20a%20position%20to%20form%20a%20government%20on%20its%20own.%20So%20a%20coalition%20government%20at%20the%20federal%20level%20is%20unavoidable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20where%20things%20get%20tricky.%20The%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%2C%20or%20PTI%20%E2%80%93%20headed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-19844270%5C%22%3Ejailed%20former%20prime%20minister%20and%20Pakistani%20cricket%20hero%20Imran%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F2%2F10%2Fwhat-comes-next-2%5C%22%3Elargest%20party%20in%20the%20national%20assembly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20around%2093%20candidates%20winning%20seats%20as%20%E2%80%9Cindependents.%E2%80%9D%20They%20had%20to%20run%20as%20independents%20because%20the%20party%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voanews.com%2Fa%2Fpakistan-s-pti-barred-from-using-cricket-bat-electoral-symbol-%2F7439552.html%5C%22%3Ebarred%20from%20using%20its%20electoral%20symbol%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20cricket%20bat%2C%20after%20a%20three-member%20bench%20of%20the%20supreme%20court%20ruled%20that%20PTI%20had%20failed%20to%20hold%20intraparty%20elections%20in%20line%20with%20its%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20a%20total%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fpakistan-vote-counts-drags-after-election-marred-by-attacks-outages-2024-02-09%2F%5C%22%3E265%20seats%20in%20parliament%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20that%20means%20the%20PTI%20is%20still%20well%20short%20of%20the%20number%20needed%20to%20form%20a%20government%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%2C%20or%20PMLN%2C%20came%20in%20second%20with%2078%20seats%2C%20a%20tally%20that%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20boosted%20by%20the%20addition%20of%20PMLN-aligned%20independent%20members%20of%20parliament.%20The%20party%20%E2%80%93%20headed%20by%20Shahbaz%20Sharif%2C%20who%20took%20over%20from%20Khan%20as%20prime%20minister%20in%202022%2C%20and%20his%20brother%2C%20former%20three-time%20prime%20minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20%E2%80%93%20is%20thought%20to%20have%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2Fworld-news%2Fpakistan-army-chief-backs-ex-pm-nawaz-sharifs-call-to-form-coalition-government%2Farticleshow%2F107587628.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ebacking%20of%20the%20powerful%20Pakistani%20army%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20did%20not%20perform%20as%20well%20as%20expected%20in%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%2C%20or%20PPP%2C%20secured%2054%20seats%2C%20placing%20it%20third.%20This%20puts%20it%20in%20a%20position%20to%20help%20another%20party%20form%20a%20coalition%20at%20the%20federal%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20the%20most%20seats%2C%20is%20the%20PTI%20the%20front-runner%20to%20lead%20a%20coalition%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20form%20a%20government%20on%20its%20own%20and%20believes%20that%20its%20mandate%20was%20stolen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20final%20election%20results%20became%20known%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fimran-khans-party-claims-victory-in-170-seats-vows-to-form-government-report-5032101%5C%22%3EPTI%20claimed%20it%20had%20won%20170%20or%20so%20seats%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20enough%20for%20it%20to%20be%20able%20to%20form%20a%20government.%20But%20that%20appears%20to%20be%20without%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20suggests%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2024%2F2%2F11%2Fpakistan-election-results-live-wait-for-final-tally-three-days-after-vote%5C%22%3EPTI%20isn%E2%80%99t%20ready%20to%20accept%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20did%20not%20get%20enough%20votes%20to%20form%20a%20government%20outright.%20The%20party%20instead%20is%20challenging%20the%20results%2C%20claiming%20that%20its%20vote%20was%20suppressed%20illegally%2C%20and%20the%20PTI%20has%20already%20formally%20registered%20complaints%20in%2018%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20believe%20it%20is%20more%20likely%20that%20a%20coalition%20will%20emerge%20between%20the%20other%20parties%2C%20led%20by%20the%20PMLN.%20But%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20that%20will%20satisfy%20an%20electorate%20that%20voted%20the%20PTI%20as%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20sound%20very%20stable.%20Is%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn%E2%80%99t.%20Pakistan%20is%20now%20entering%20an%20uncertain%20scenario%2C%20which%20is%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20a%20post-election%20political%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECoalitions%20are%20not%20uncommon%20in%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20politics%2C%20but%20they%20are%20not%20easy%20to%20manage.%20They%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usip.org%2Fpublications%2F2022%2F08%2Fpakistans-new-government-struggles-consolidate-control%5C%22%3Ebecome%20unwieldy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAtlanticCouncil%2Fstatus%2F1756069234101133713%5C%22%3Eweak%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarnegieendowment.org%2F2023%2F05%2F10%2Fmilitary-disrupts-pakistan-s-democracy-once-again-pub-89724%5C%22%3Eprone%20to%20manipulation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20makes%20it%20far%20harder%20for%20any%20government%20to%20push%20through%20the%20kind%20of%20bold%20economic%20packages%20needed%20for%20the%20country%20to%20move%20forward%20and%20escape%20the%20deep%20structural%20problems%20that%20are%20ailing%20the%20economy%2C%20such%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theigc.org%2Fblogs%2Ftaxing-effectively%2Fwhy-does-pakistan-tax-so-little%5C%22%3Elimited%20tax%20base%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reliance%20on%20handouts%20from%20other%20countries.%20Tackling%20that%20requires%20hard%2C%20potentially%20unpopular%20decisions%2C%20which%20are%20more%20difficult%20when%20a%20government%20is%20split%20and%20has%20a%20limited%20popular%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20may%20need%20another%20national%20vote%20before%20too%20long%20to%20secure%20a%20more%20stable%20and%20workable%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20election%20has%20been%20called%20flawed%20in%20the%20West.%20Is%20that%20fair%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20standards%2C%20the%20actual%20polling%20went%20off%20relatively%20peacefully.%20There%20was%20a%20terrible%20attack%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Flive-news%2F20240118-baluchistan-explosive-region-on-iran-pakistan-borderland%5C%22%3Erestive%20province%20of%20Baluchistan%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20election%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-68226516%5C%22%3Ekilled%2028%20people%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20fears%20of%20widespread%20violence%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20election%20did%20not%20materialise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20there%20were%20undue%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fpakistan-election-human-rights-commission-khan-3258e2131ac83e89c2c376b476caccec%5C%22%3Ecurbs%20on%20political%20activity%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apstylebook.com%2Fsearch%3Fquery%3Drunup%26button%3D%5C%22%3Erun-up%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20election%20itself%20appears%20to%20be%20largely%20credible%20by%20Pakistani%20standards%2C%20as%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Farticles%2F2024-02-10%2Fpakistan-hits-back-at-criticism-of-election-conduct-and-insists-cellphone-curbs-were-necessary%5C%22%3Equick%20to%20attest%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20PTI%2C%20a%20party%20that%20is%20out%20of%20favour%20with%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20current%20senior%20military%20leadership%2C%20has%20done%20so%20well%20suggests%20there%20was%20no%20straightforward%20rigging%20across%20the%20board.%20There%20was%20harassment%20of%20PTI%20voters%20in%20some%20places%2C%20but%20it%20clearly%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20sufficient%20to%20make%20huge%20inroads%20into%20their%20overall%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20can%E2%80%99t%20compare%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20democracy%20with%20that%20of%20the%20U.S.%20or%20any%20other%20country.%20The%20problem%20with%20many%20outside%20observers%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20politics%20is%20that%20they%20talk%20normatively%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%2C%20they%20see%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20elections%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20what%20is%20generally%20seen%20as%20the%20norm%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Pakistani%20politics%20are%20unique.%20The%20country%20is%20a%20military-dominated%20state%2C%20with%20generals%20that%20have%20long%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F02%2F04%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fpakistan-election-imran-khan.html%5C%22%3Eand%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20alternative%20to%20managed%20elections%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20messy%2C%20is%20martial%20law.%20And%20a%20flawed%20democracy%20is%20better%20than%20the%20military%20jackboot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20that%2C%20the%20election%20itself%20took%20place%20relatively%20peacefully.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20criticism%20in%20the%20West%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F2%2F8%2Finherently-undemocratic-pakistan-suspends-mobile-services-on-voting-day%5C%22%3Ecellphones%20and%20mobile%20internet%20services%20being%20blocked%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20election%20day.%20That%20may%20seem%20like%20unacceptable%20interference%20in%20the%20electoral%20process%20to%20outside%20observers.%20But%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20there%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrance24.com%2Fen%2F20121123-pakistan-suspends-mobile-phone-service-security-ashura-shiite-terrorism%5C%22%3Ereal%20concern%20about%20cellphones%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20used%20to%20detonate%20explosive%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20anyone%20be%20pleased%20with%20the%20election%20result%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20while%20the%20PTI%E2%80%99s%20strong%20showing%20represents%20an%20anti-establishment%20vote%20%E2%80%93%20and%2C%20more%20specifically%2C%20an%20anti-army%20vote%20%E2%80%93%20the%20divided%20national%20mandate%20means%20the%20army%20high%20command%20has%20reason%20to%20be%20satisfied%20with%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20split%20national%20assembly%20and%20weak%20government%20plays%20into%20the%20military%E2%80%99s%20hands.%20Should%20the%20PMLN%20govern%20as%20the%20major%20party%20in%20a%20coalition%2C%20it%20will%20be%20in%20a%20position%20of%20relative%20weakness%20and%20will%20need%20the%20army%E2%80%99s%20support%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20PTI%20engages%20in%20widespread%20protests%20against%20the%20election%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20there%20any%20positives%20from%20the%20election%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20insofar%20as%20the%20process%20of%20seeking%20the%20peoples%E2%80%99%20support%20has%20been%20allowed%20to%20continue.%20But%20the%20negatives%20are%20seen%20by%20most%20to%20outweigh%20the%20positives%20and%20the%202024%20elections%20are%20being%20viewed%20as%20equally%20%E2%80%93%20if%20not%20more%20%E2%80%93%20manipulated%20and%20controlled%20than%20the%202018%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turnout%20this%20time%20around%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nation.com.pk%2F10-Feb-2024%2Fvoters-turnout-remain-48-percent-in-election-fafen-report%5C%22%3Eestimated%20to%20be%20around%2048%25%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20lower%20than%20in%202018%20when%20it%20was%2051%25.%20The%20demographic%20breakdown%20is%20encouraging.%20The%20youth%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%3B%2044%25%20of%20voters%20were%20under%20the%20age%20of%2035.%20And%20women%2C%20too%2C%20played%20a%20larger%20role%20in%20the%20vote%20%E2%80%93%20more%20women%20contested%20and%20also%20won%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20party%20politics%20aside%2C%20the%20result%20suggests%20that%20old%20tactics%20to%20intimidate%20and%20suppress%20voters%20largely%20didn%E2%80%99t%20work.%20The%20expectation%20was%20that%20the%20spate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fmain-criminal-cases-against-pakistans-imran-khan-2024-01-31%2F%5C%22%3Elegal%20verdicts%20against%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20weeks%20before%20the%20election%20and%20his%20continued%20imprisonment%20might%20curb%20his%20popularity%20and%20mean%20PTI%20supporters%20would%20stay%20home.%20That%20clearly%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20they%20helped%20deliver%20may%20only%20help%20continue%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20political%20malaise%20as%20it%20heads%20into%20a%20new%2C%20uncertain%20period.%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Conversation%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcounter.theconversation.com%2Fcontent%2F223287%2Fcount.gif%3Fdistributor%3Drepublish-lightbox-basic%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAyesha%20Jalal%2C%20Professor%20of%20History%2C%20Tufts%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20licence.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%