7568107298648358%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinwar%2C%2061%2C%20is%20a%20former%20commander%20of%20Hamas's%20Ezzdine%20al-Qassam%20Brigades%20and%20was%20elected%20in%202017%20as%20the%20Palestinian%20group's%20head.%20He%20has%20spent%2023%20years%20in%20Israeli%20jails%20before%20his%20release%20in%202011%20in%20a%20prisoner%20exchange%20involving%20French-Israeli%20soldier%20Gilad%20Shalit%20who%20was%20held%20captive%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20retrieved%20from%20Hamas%20surveillance%20footage%20recently%20obtained%20by%20IDF%20troops%2C%20shows%20Sinwar%20appearing%20healthy%20and%20carrying%20a%20bag%20while%20his%20daughter%20holds%20a%20doll.%20The%20IDF%20claims%20that%20the%20footage%20was%20taken%20from%20tunnels%20that%20connect%20to%20areas%20where%20hostages%20were%20held%2C%20and%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20network%20used%20by%20senior%20Hamas%20officials%20during%20the%20recent%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIDF%20spokesman%20Daniel%20Hagari%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20video%20or%20another%20is%20not%20what%20really%20matters.%20What%20is%20important%20is%20the%20intelligence%20that%20will%20allow%20us%20to%20reach%20senior%20Hamas%20officials%20and%20the%20hostages.%20The%20hunt%20for%20Sinwar%20will%20not%20stop%20until%20we%20catch%20him%2C%20dead%20or%20alive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHagari%20also%20claimed%20that%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Israeli%20troops%20detained%20close%20relatives%20of%20senior%20Hamas%20military%20commanders%2C%20including%20Sinwar.%20Among%20those%20detained%20were%20the%20father%20of%20Rafa'a%20Salameh%2C%20the%20commander%20of%20Hamas's%20Rafah%20Brigade%2C%20and%20the%20son%20of%20Husni%20Hamdan%2C%20another%20senior%20Hamas%20commander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IDF%20conducted%20raids%20in%20the%20tunnel%20network%20seen%20in%20the%20October%2010%20footage%2C%20situated%20under%20a%20cemetery%20in%20the%20Bani%20Suheila%20area%20of%20Khan%20Younis.%20According%20to%20Hagari%2C%20the%20tunnels%20contained%20bedrooms%20of%20senior%20Hamas%20officials%20and%20the%20office%20of%20the%20commander%20of%20the%20Khan%20Younis%20Brigade's%20Eastern%20Battalion%2C%20who%20directed%20the%20October%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707896160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fpo353vqo_sinwar-_625x300_14_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-idf-video-hamas-commander-yahya-sinwar-who-orchestrated-october-7-attack-spotted-in-tunnel-5055275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20released%20footage%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20claiming%20to%20have%20identified%20Hamas%20leader%20Yahya%20Sinwar%20walking%20through%20a%20Gaza%20tunnel%20with%20his%20family%20members.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-idf-video-hamas-commander-yahya-sinwar-who-orchestrated-october-7-attack-spotted-in-tunnel-5055275%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-idf-video-hamas-commander-yahya-sinwar-who-orchestrated-october-7-attack-spotted-in-tunnel-5055275%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-gaza-palestine-idf-video-hamas-commander-yahya-sinwar-who-orchestrated-october-7-attack-spotted-in-tunnel-5055275%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Democrats%20flip%20seat%20of%20disgraced%20New%20York%20congressman%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707896126000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107684363%2Cimgsize-133490.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdemocrats-flip-seat-of-disgrace