.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReuters%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20the%20trade%20ministry%20as%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findias-agricultural-exports-rise-despite-curbs-wheat-rice-sugar-minister-2024-01-08%2F%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20agricultural%20exports%20will%20rise%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202023-2024%20from%20last%20year%20despite%20curbs%20on%20wheat%2C%20rice%20and%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20second-largest%20producer%20of%20wheat%2C%20rice%20and%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707891103000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2F01175204%2Fagriculture.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findias-agricultural-exports-on-path-of-continuing-decline-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20a%20report%20on%20The%20New%20Indian%20Express%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20agri-export%20growth%20rate%20was%206%25%20in%202022-2023.%20But%20it%20was%2017%25%20in%202020-2021.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findias-agricultural-exports-on-path-of-continuing-decline-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SpaceX%20postpones%20launch%20of%20intuitive%20machines%20Moon%20mission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707890145000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107681061%2Cimgsize-1046764.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fspacex-postpones-launch-of-intuitive-machines-moon-mission%2Farticleshow%2F107680845.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107680845.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20spacecraft%2C%20built%20by%20Intu