a%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2FFeb%2F13%2Fdalit-groom-forced-off-horse-in-gujarat-wedding-procession-faces-caste-abuse%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20four%20individuals%20under%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20from%20the%20groom%E2%80%99s%20brother%20and%20cousin.%20The%20complaint%20states%20that%20the%20groom%20was%20riding%20a%20horse%20as%20part%20of%20his%20%3Cem%3Ebaarat%3C%2Fem%3E%20around%201%20pm%20and%20passing%20through%20the%20village%20when%20a%20motorcyclist%20threatened%20the%20groom%2C%20forcibly%20removed%20him%20from%20the%20horse%2C%20and%20uttered%20casteist%20slurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20my%20brother%20was%20forcibly%20removed%20from%20the%20horse%2C%20our%20family%20members%20attempted%20to%20resolve%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20individual.%20During%20this%2C%20three%20other%20people%20intervened%2C%20siding%20with%20the%20person%20who%20removed%20my%20brother%20from%20the%20horse%2C%20and%20subjected%20us%20to%20caste-based%20abuse.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20family%20member%20was%20slapped%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20groom%E2%80%99s%20brother%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20claimed%20riding%20a%20horse%20required%20their%20permission.%20Despite%20my%20efforts%20for%20a%20peaceful%20procession%2C%20they%20refused%20to%20budge%20and%20instead%20threatened%20the%20horse%20owner%20and%20DJ%20sound%20personnel%20to%20leave%20the%20wedding%20venue%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20stay%20in%20your%20limits%E2%80%A6you%20can%E2%80%99t%20ride%20a%20horse.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20you%20know%20the%20tradition%20of%20the%20village%3F%20You%20have%20to%20seek%20permission%20from%20us%20and%20only%20Thakors%20can%20ride%20horses%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20accused%20allegedly%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fgujarat%2Fgujarat-dalit-groom-assaulted-for-riding-horse-during-wedding-told-to-stay-within-limits-2893098%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Chronicle%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Gandhinagar%20Kalol%20Division%20Praveen%20Manwar%20told%20the%20media%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20wedding%20procession%20in%20Chadasana%20village%20of%20Mansa%20went%20with%20a%20DJ%20sound%20system%2C%20three%20people%20from%20the%20village%20opposed%20it%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20clash%20with%20two%20parties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20clash%20began%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20playing%20the%20DJ%20sound%2C%20and%20then%20there%20was%20a%20dispute%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20sitting%20on%20the%20horse.%20The%20police%20have%20filed%20an%20FIR%20on%20this%20matter%2C%20and%20the%20police%20have%20also%20rounded%20up%20those%20named%20as%20accused%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdalit-groom-assaulted-for-riding-horse-during-wedding-procession-in-gujarat-5052034%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20NDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20four%20arrested%20are%20Sailesh%20Thakore%2C%20Jayesh%20Thakore%2C%20Samir%20Thakore%20and%20Ashwin%20Thakore.%20All%20four%20are%20from%20an%20OBC%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20such%20instances%20of%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20violence%20specifically%20involving%20Dalit%20grooms%20continue%20to%20be%20reported%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707887128000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14103350%2FScreenshot-2024-02-14-at-10.32.40-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fgujarat-dalit-groom-allegedly-forced-off-horse-abused-with-slurs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fgujarat-dalit-groom-allegedly-forced-off-horse-abused-with-slurs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Over%203000%20Babies%20With%20Congenital%20Heart%20Diseases%20Have%20Been%20Saved%20By%20This%20Inspiring%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahida%20Khatoon%20(26)%20remembers%2022%20February%2C%202023%2C%20like%20it%20was%20yesterday%2C%20as%20she%20welcomed%20her%20first%20child%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306675%2Fanindita-chatterjee-travel-content-creator-new-mom-travelling-with-infant-pregnancy-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaby%20boy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20into%20the%20world.%20She%20was%20discharged%20from%20the%20hospital%20after%20eight%20days%20and%20was%20all%20set%20for%20the%20trials%20and%20tribulations%20that%20a%20new%20mother%20has%20to%20face.%20But%20two%20days%20after%20she%20went%20home%20with%20her%20bundle%20of%20joy%2C%20the%20concerned%20Kolkata%20resident%20started%20noticing%20alarming%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2010-day-old%20baby%20was%20turning%20blue%20when%20he%20cried.%20They%20immediately%20rushed%20to%20a%20doctor%2C%20who%20diagnosed%20that%20there%20might%20be%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20heart%2C%20and%20advised%20the%20parents%20to%20take%20the%20baby%20to%20a%20bigger%20hospital.%20Wahida%20recounts%20that%20her%20son%20was%20then%20diagnosed%20with%20Congenital%20Heart%20Disease%20(CHD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECHDs%20are%20present%20at%20birth%20and%20can%20affect%20the%20structure%20of%20a%20baby%E2%80%99s%20heart%20and%20the%20way%20it%20works.%20They%20can%20affect%20how%20blood%20flows%20through%20the%20heart%20and%20out%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20body.%20CHDs%20can%20vary%20from%20mild%20(such%20as%20a%20small%20hole%20in%20the%20heart)%20to%20severe%20(such%20as%20missing%20or%20poorly%20formed%20parts%20of%20the%20heart).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F30745481%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Library%20of%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%20stated%20that%20nine%20out%20of%201%2C000%20babies%20have%20CHD.%20In%20India%2C%20more%20than%20two%20lakh%20babies%20are%20estimated%20to%20have%20this%20condition%20annually.%20One-fifth%20of%20these%20babies%20will%20likely%20need%20intervention%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20their%20life%2C%20due%20to%20a%20serious%20birth%20defect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%2C%20though%2C%20is%20twofold%2C%20as%20early%20and%20timely%20intervention%20is%20of%20prime%20importance%20in%20this%20disease.%20But%20specialised%20care%20is%20lacking%20in%20most%20government%20institutions%2C%20which%20causes%20a%20financial%20constraint%20on%20parents%20with%20low%20incomes%2C%20like%20Wahida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahida%20found%20help%20through%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20a%20charitable%20trust%2C%20which%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20has%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20timely%20intervention%20is%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20a%20charitable%20trust%2C%20which%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20has%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1707842491-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341760%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20has%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarted%20in%202009%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20works%20for%20the%20health%20and%20well-being%20of%20marginalised%20and%20rural%20communities.%20As%20the%20foundation%20worked%20closely%20with%20children%20and%20persons%20with%20disabilities%2C%20it%20soon%20realised%20the%20need%20for%20better%20medical%20facilities%20and%20early%20intervention%20for%20the%20underprivileged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interactions%20with%20doctors%2C%20they%20found%20that%20a%20major%20area%20which%20needed%20attention%20was%20CHD%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20common%20birth%20defects%20in%20newborns.%20The%20Global%20Burden%20of%20Disease%20Study%202017%20found%20that%20CHD%20was%20the%20seventh%20biggest%20contributor%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261889%2Fjharkhand-reduce-infant-maternal-mortality-rate-doctor-couple-quits-job%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20infant%20mortality%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20caused%201.8%20lakh%20infant%20deaths%20in%202017.%20As%20such%2C%20in%202013%2C%20the%20foundation%20started%20working%20to%20provide%20aid%20for%20surgical%20interventions%20for%20children%20born%20with%20congenital%20heart%20defects%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20leading%20hospitals%20in%20the%20country%2C%20under%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%20Program%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCongenital%20Heart%20Disease%20(CHD)%20holds%20the%20foremost%20position%20globally%20in%20causing%20deaths%20linked%20to%20birth%20defects%2C%20persisting%20as%20a%20significant%20contributor%20to%20mortality%20and%20morbidity%20in%20both%20paediatric%20populations%20of%20developing%20and%20developed%20nations.%20In%20India%20only%2C%20it%20accounts%20for%2010%20percent%20of%20infant%20deaths%2C%20despite%20notable%20advancements%20in%20diagnosing%20and%20treating%20CHDs%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Viresh%20Mahajan%2C%20Director%20of%20Paediatric%20Cardiac%20Sciences%20%26amp%3B%20Scientific%20Director%20of%20Clinical%20Research%2C%20Sarvodaya%20Hospital%2C%20Faridabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetecting%20congenital%20heart%20disease%20is%20possible%20during%20prenatal%20and%20postnatal%20stages%20through%20diverse%20diagnostic%20methods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTime%20sensitivity%20is%20critical%2C%20as%20any%20delay%20can%20prove%20fatal%20for%20infants.%20Timely%20treatment%20is%20very%20important%20as%20a%20child%20can%20lead%20a%20normal%20life%20in%20most%20congenital%20heart%20defects%20if%20treated%20at%20the%20optimal%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20state%20that%20early%20intervention%20is%20key.%20Dr%20Mahajan%20adds%20that%20children%20with%20CHD%20can%20lead%20healthy%20and%20lengthy%20lives%20with%20early%20identification%20and%20prompt%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Early%20intervention%20is%20of%20prime%20importance%20in%20CHD%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-585-min-1707842489-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341759%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEarly%20intervention%20is%20of%20prime%20importance%20in%20CHD%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Vishal%20Changela%2C%20Paediatric%20Interventional%20Cardiologist%20at%20SGVP%20Holistic%20Hospital%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20states%20that%20only%20some%20patients%20with%20CHD%20need%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20patients%20just%20need%20medications%20and%20follow-up.%2090%20percent%20of%20children%20with%20CHD%20can%20lead%20a%20normal%20life%20with%20timely%20intervention.%20The%20problem%20lies%20with%20the%20time%20of%20diagnosis.%20If%20done%20early%2C%20we%20can%20act%20immediately%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20diagnosis%20is%20not%20done%20on%20time%2C%20Dr%20Changela%20has%20seen%20cases%20of%20adults%20with%20irreversible%20damage%20to%20the%20heart%20and%20lung%2C%20in%20which%20cases%20only%20palliative%20care%20is%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurgical%20care%20has%20also%20evolved%20with%20hospitals%20seeing%20success%20rates%20close%20to%2098%20percent%2C%20according%20to%20Dr%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERBSK%20(Rashtriya%20Bal%20Swasthya%20Karyakram)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20national%20initiative%20to%20screen%20and%20treat%20childhood%20diseases%20and%20disabilities%2C%20including%20CHD%20has%20been%20running%20since%202012.%20Yet%2C%20lack%20of%20awareness%20prevents%20women%20from%20going%20for%20antenatal%20screenings%20and%20screenings%20after%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20advanced%20diagnosis%20and%20treatment%2C%20CHD%20still%20remains%20largely%20undiagnosed%20or%20is%20diagnosed%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20too%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20happens%20in%20cases%20like%20Wahida%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20who%20was%20diagnosed%20on%20time%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20alertness%20of%20the%20parents%2C%20but%20faced%20with%20a%20massive%20bill%20of%20over%20Rs%203%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20treated%20at%20a%20government%20hospital%2C%20Wahida%20was%20asked%20to%20visit%20a%20specialist%20at%20a%20private%20hospital%2C%20R%20N%20Tagore%20Hospital%2C%20Kolkata.%20Here%2C%20the%20doctor%20assessed%20the%20baby%20and%20diagnosed%20him%20with%20a%20Ventricular%20Septal%20Defect%20(VSD)%2C%20which%20needed%20surgery.%20The%20surgery%20(done%20when%20the%20baby%20was%201.5%20months%20old)%20would%20cost%20over%20Rs%203.5%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahida%E2%80%99s%20husband%2C%20Aslan%2C%20works%20as%20a%20salesman%20with%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%20per%20annum.%20As%20they%20explained%20their%20situation%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20they%20got%20help%20through%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20which%20financially%20supported%20the%20surgery.%20The%20baby%20also%20needed%20an%20open%20heart%20surgery%20in%20January%202024%2C%20which%20would%20cost%20Rs%204.8%20lakh.%20This%20too%2C%20was%20supported%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20the%20timely%20intervention%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F298516%2Fengineer-quits-job-to-make-natural-baby-food-mixes-earns-lakhs-tummy-friendly-sridevi-ashala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebaby%20is%20now%20well%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20meeting%20all%20his%20milestones%20just%20like%20any%20other%20infant%2C%20says%20Wahida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESaving%203%2C000%20lives%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Hans%20Foundation%20has%20partnered%20with%2015%20hospitals%20across%20the%20country.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492-1536x864.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-575-1707842492-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341761%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20has%20partnered%20with%2015%20hospitals%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20is%20working%20on%20solving%20the%20financial%20problems%20as%20these%20surgeries%20are%20very%20expensive%20for%20the%20common%20man.%20But%20this%20one%20surgery%20can%20save%20a%20child%20and%20improve%20their%20quality%20of%20life.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20CHD%20requires%20immediate%20paediatric%20cardiac%20care%2C%20either%20in%20the%20first%20month%20or%20first%20year%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20certain%20instances%2C%20surgery%20may%20be%20imperative%20within%20the%20initial%20hours%20or%20days%20of%20the%20child%E2%80%99s%20life.%20Hence%2C%20early%20diagnosis%20and%20timely%20management%20stand%20as%20pivotal%20elements%20in%20the%20treatment%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Foundation%20has%20partnered%20with%2015%20hospitals%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20National%20Heart%20Institute%2C%20Wockhardt%20Hospital%2C%20Fortis%2C%20Apollo%2C%20The%20Narayana%20Group%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20across%20the%20country.%20So%20far%2C%20they%20have%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD%20get%20surgery%20as%20soon%20as%20required%20%E2%80%94%20including%20a%2026-day-old%20baby.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foundation%20provides%20this%20financial%20support%20to%20patients%20with%20an%20annual%20income%20below%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20and%20children%20below%20the%20age%20of%2020.%20The%20Little%20Hearts%20Programme%20supports%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20surgeries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20procedures%20such%20as%20Atrial%20Septal%20Defect%20(ASD)%2C%20Ventricular%20Septal%20Defect%20(VSD)%2C%20Tetralogy%20of%20Fallot%20(ToF)%20and%20more%20complex%20surgeries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20providing%20immediate%20financial%20assistance%2C%20the%20foundation%20also%20offers%20post-surgery%20care%2C%20which%20is%20equally%20vital.%20In%20cases%20where%20parents%20are%20unable%20to%20afford%20medications%20or%20specialist%20fees%2C%20the%20foundation%20extends%20support.%20Moreover%2C%20they%20conduct%20awareness%20programmes%20in%20collaboration%20with%20hospitals%20to%20ensure%20that%20parents%20are%20knowledgeable%20about%20symptoms%20and%20know%20when%20to%20seek%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CParents%20should%20remain%20vigilant%20and%20not%20overlook%20common%20congenital%20heart%20disease%20(CHD)%20symptoms%20in%20newborns%2C%20including%20challenges%20in%20feeding%2C%20rapid%20breathing%2C%20or%20bluish%20skin%20discolouration%2C%20as%20early%20recognition%20is%20crucial%20for%20timely%20intervention%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Mahajan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20response%20to%20the%20programme%20and%20with%20an%20intention%20to%20help%20more%20children%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20is%20now%20expanding%20its%20intervention%20under%20The%20Hans%20Paediatric%20Care%20programme%20that%20will%20focus%20on%20various%20aspects%20of%20child%20health.%20It%20hopes%20to%20partner%20with%20more%20hospitals%20to%20provide%20financial%20access%20to%20families%20and%20build%20a%20world%20where%20every%20child%20has%20equal%20access%20to%20quality%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20parents%20like%20Wahida%2C%20this%20financial%20assistance%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20through%20such%20a%20tough%20time%20when%20I%20suddenly%20discovered%20that%20my%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261081%2Findia-buy-online-ergonomic-baby-carrier-cost-features-woman-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E10-day-old%20baby%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20heart%20problem.%20While%20I%20got%20the%20diagnosis%20soon%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20to%20arrange%20the%20money.%20My%20baby%20is%20hale%20and%20healthy%20today%2C%20all%20thanks%20to%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Wahida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20surgery%2C%20babies%20can%20lead%20a%20normal%20life.%20What%20advice%20does%20Dr%20Changela%20give%20hi