0%20reject%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20nation-wide%20caste%20census%2C%20because%20you%20fear%20that%20measure%20might%20overturn%C2%A0%20your%20upper%20caste%20applecart%20which%20continues%20to%20deny%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20Hindus%20the%20just%20fruits%20of%20their%20labour%2C%20and%20their%20right%20to%20equality%20under%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20I%20hope%20that%20those%20who%20venerate%20me%20will%20not%20be%20taken%20in%20by%20your%C2%A0disingenuous%C2%A0%20subterfuge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EChaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20clever%20of%20you%3B%20how%20very%20clever%20of%20you%20to%20have%20thus%C2%A0co-opted%20me%2C%20me%20who%20was%20principally%20responsible%20for%20bringing%20down%20the%20Janata%20government%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20dual%20membership%20of%20some%20of%20its%20constituents%2C%20demanding%20that%20they%20either%20be%20in%20government%20or%20out%20of%20it%20as%20members%20of%20the%20RSS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20you%20truly%20think%20my%20followers%20will%20forget%20that%20my%20entire%20political%20career%20was%20informed%20by%20a%20resolute%20rejection%20of%20sectarian%20politics%20which%20you%20practice%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20how%20cynical%20of%20you%20to%20imagine%20I%20did%20not%20see%20what%20you%20did%20to%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation%20over%20a%20year-long%20period%20of%20time%2C%C2%A0%20during%20which%20some%20750%20of%20them%20sacrificed%20their%20lives%20for%20their%20cause%20which%20you%20did%20not%20grant.%20Are%20my%20followers%20to%20think%20that%20bestowing%20thus%20honour%20on%20me%20has%20helped%20lower%20the%20cost%20of%20farm%20inputs%2C%20or%20hiked%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20income%20from%20a%20grand%20Rs%2027%20a%20day%20to%20even%2030%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22For%20'Bharat%20Ratna'%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%2C%20Politics%20Meant%20the%20Art%20of%20the%20Possible%5C%2