southern%20states%20because%20of%20my%20identity%20%E2%80%93%20disgraceful%20beyond%20words.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENarasimha%20Rao%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CThat%20I%20am%20reviled%20to%20this%20day%20for%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20five-centuries-old%20mosque%20in%20Ayodhya%20(that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20called%20a%20%E2%80%98criminal%E2%80%99%20act)%20owes%20entirely%20to%20the%20unethical%20fact%20that%20you%20made%20a%20promise%20on%20an%20affidavit%20to%20the%20highest%20court%20in%20the%20land%20that%20you%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20mosque%20to%20be%20damaged%20at%20any%20cost.%20How%20you%20betrayed%20me%20in%20the%20deepest%20consequence%2C%20ever%20to%20taint%20my%20otherwise%20illustrious%20career%2C%20even%20as%20you%20accused%20me%20of%20having%C2%A0%20purchased%20votes%20to%20save%20my%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20do%20you%20think%20I%20am%20not%20cognisant%20of%20the%20latest%20perfidy%20on%20your%20behalf%3F%20That%20lauding%20me%20for%20having%20opened%20up%20the%20economy%2C%20you%20should%20bring%20a%20%3Cem%3EWhite%20Paper%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0to%20parliament%2C%20deriding%20everything%20that%20my%20policies%20had%20achieved%20for%20the%20republic%20over%20ten%20long%20years%2C%20making%20possible%20your%20own%20further%20efforts%20to%20build%20on%20what%C2%A0%20my%20UPA%20government%C2%A0%20had%20set%20in%20motion%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20keep%20tom-tomming%20how%20you%20have%20made%20the%20economy%20fifth%C2%A0largest%20globally%2C%20concealing%20the%20all-important%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20under%20Manmohan%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20stewardship%20of%20the%20finance%20ministry%20in%20my%20cabinet%20that%20we%20pulled%20up%20our%20GDP%20three-fold%C2%A0%C2%A0from%20%24609%20billion%20to%20%242.1%20trillion%20at%20an%20average%20growth%20rate%20of%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%2010%20years%20since%20my%20party%20left%20office%20in%202014%2C%20you%20have%20raised%20that%20number%C2%A0%20only%20to%20%243.3%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20fool%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoes%20it%20please%20me%20that%20in%20honouring%20me%20your%20chief%20purpose%20has%20been%20to%20snub%20the%20party%20to%20which%20I%20belonged%20all%20my%20life%3F%C2%A0%20You%20assume%20too%20much%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDo%20I%20not%20understand%20that%20you%20seek%20to%20use%20me%20now%20to%20better%20your%20prospects%20in%20the%20Telugu%20regions%20of%20the%20country%3F%20But%20do%20not%20think%20that%20those%20who%20speak%20my%20language%20and%20share%20my%20culture%20will%20be%20so%20easily%20fooled.%20They%20know%20your%20reality%20lies%20in%20imposing%20Hindi%20on%20India%20below%20the%20Vindhyas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20always%20say%20how%20erudite%20I%20was%3B%20indeed%3B%20so%20I%20grin%2C%20but%20am%20not%20taken%20in.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22A%20Bharat%20Ratna%20a%20Week%20for%20the%20Next%20Two%20Months%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhumour%2Fa-bharat-ratna-a-week-for-the-next-two-months%5C%22%3EA%20Bharat%20Ratna%20a%20Week%20for%20the%20Next%20Two%20Months%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EL.K.%20Advani%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWho%20has%20better%20knowledge%20of%20you%2C%20my%20young%20friend%2C%20than%20this%20relegated%20old%20man%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20decades%20now%2C%20you%20put%20me%20on%20the%20shelf%2C%20indeed%2C%20in%20the%20cupboard%2C%20and%20now%20pull%20me%20out%20to%20bring%20back%20the%20active%20participation%20of%20older%20workers%20of%20the%20right-wing%20who%20have%20been%20disaffected%20with%20you%3B%20how%20well%20I%20know%20this%20to%20be%20the%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20also%20know%2C%20knowing%20you%20so%20well%2C%20that%20you%20may%20yet%20bestow%20some%20more%20%3Cem%3ERatnas%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20entice%20sections%20of%20the%20populace%20whose%20favour%20you%20have%20lost.%20The%20names%20of%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray%2C%20Kashi%20Ram%20Ji%2C%20for%20example%2C%20come%20to%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20compliment%20I%20do%20give%20you%3A%20that%20over%20the%20years%20you%20have%20come%20to%20best%20your%20mentor%20to%20an%20extent%20and%20in%20ways%20that%20I%2C%20your%20mentor%2C%20may%20not%20have%20imagined.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20together%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20will%20our%20elevation%20to%20speechless%20totems%20serve%20your%20crude%20political%20purpose%3F%20Alas%2C%20it%20well%20may.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20nation%20that%20likes%20deities%20rather%20than%20human%20subjects%2C%20that%20celebrates%20power%20rather%20than%20freedom%20of%20thought%2C%20that%20treats%20slogans%20raised%20by%20autocrats%20as%20%C2%A0achieved%20results%2C%20that%20is%20quick%20to%20rally%20given%20a%20sense%20of%20its%20%C2%A0alleged%20victimhood%2C%20that%20follows%20a%20cult%20in%20power%20to%20the%20ends%20of%20the%20earth%20to%20seek%20out%20some%20newly%20constructed%20enemy%2C%20that%20values%20a%20paroxysm%20of%20emotion%20over%20rational%20poise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20in%20return%20for%20the%20honour%20bestowed%20on%20us%2C%20%C2%A0we%20give%20to%20you%20the%20award%20of%20having%C2%A0%20%C2%A0pulverised%20the%20common%20mind%20away%20%C2%A0from%C2%A0%C2%A0fact%20and%20reason%2C%20more%20than%20the%20greatest%20of%20magicians%20the%20world%20has%20known%2C%20not%20excluding%20Houdini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20day%20nonetheless%20does%20come%20when%20cheated%20and%20mesmerised%20innocence%20realises%20the%20swindle.%20Then%20the%20rage%20of%20the%20%C2%A0reawakened%20%C2%A0retrieves%20lost%20causes%20as%20nothing%20else%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPerhaps%20we%20are%20not%20there%20yet%2C%20alas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fbadri-raina%5C%22%3EBadri%20Raina%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0taugh