20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20Free%20Movement%20Regime%20(FMR)%20with%20Myanmar%20will%20be%20discontinued%20on%20February%206%20has%20added%20a%20layer%20of%20complexity%20to%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20dynamics.%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20regarding%20the%20fencing%20of%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border%20has%20sparked%20mixed%20reactions.%20While%20it%20addresses%20a%20longstanding%20demand%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20majority%20Meitei%20community%2C%20it%20has%20left%20the%20Kuki%20community%20disheartened.%20Sharing%20ethnic%20ties%20with%20communities%20across%20the%20border%20in%20Myanmar%2C%20the%20Kuki%20community%20views%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20FMR%20as%20detrimental%20to%20their%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707879730000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F14083053%2FGF6N9qFWcAA16U2.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-two-more-men-killed-on-tuesday-4-day-power-outage-in-saikul-district%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manipur%20has%20been%20facing%20ethnic%20violence%20and%20intense%20social%20divisions%20since%20May%203%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-two-more-men-killed-on-tuesday-4-day-power-outage-in-saikul-district%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nigeria%20cost%20of%20living%3A%20People%20turn%20to%20'throw-away'%20rice%20for%20food%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707878951000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F6435%2Fproduction%2F_132635652_whatsappimage2024-02-13at15.54.07-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68272830%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAfafata%26quot%3B%20rice%20is%20usually%20discarded%20but%20rising%20prices%20mean%20many%20northern%20fami