Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fthe-sawantwadi-palace-2-1707824518-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fthe-sawantwadi-palace-2-1707824518-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fthe-sawantwadi-palace-2-1707824518-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fthe-sawantwadi-palace-2-1707824518-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341659%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20artisans%20who%20are%20closely%20associated%20with%20the%20Sawantwadi%20Palace%20are%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20preserving%20the%20%3Cem%3Eganjifa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eart%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20The%20Sawant%20Bhonsle%20family%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20thus%2C%20the%20couple%20got%20started%20%E2%80%94%20Shraddha%E2%80%99s%20culinary%20prowess%20and%20Lakham%E2%80%99s%20natural%20instinct%20for%20art%2C%20a%20combination%20that%20unveiled%20the%20lost%20grandeur%20of%20the%2018th-century%20palace.%20For%20Lakham%2C%20the%20part%20he%20thoroughly%20enjoyed%20was%20seeing%20life%20being%20breathed%20back%20into%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20place%20he%20calls%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%2C%20before%20India%20got%20independence%2C%20there%20used%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20would%20come%20to%20the%20palace%20to%20meet%20my%20grandfather.%20There%20would%20be%20activities%20going%20on%2C%20chatter%20and%20laughter.%20But%20in%20recent%20years%20my%20family%20were%20the%20only%20ones%20living%20here.%20Palaces%20are%20built%20for%20people.%20The%20human%20energy%20was%20missing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20the%20homestay%2C%20was%20an%20attempt%20at%20bringing%20it%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20deciding%20to%20restore%20the%20palace%20quarters%20to%20hosting%20their%20first%20guests%20in%2