t%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAastha%20and%20Vaibhav%20Patel%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vaibhav%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%205%2C707%20hectares%20of%20land%20under%20saffron%20cultivation%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20more%20than%2090%20percent%20is%20in%20the%20Pampore%20tehsil%20of%20Pulwama%20district%20in%20South%20Kashmir.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20Valley%20rejoiced%20as%20the%20GI%20tag%20was%20given%20to%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20making%20it%20illegal%20for%20someone%20outside%20the%20valley%20to%20make%20and%20sell%20a%20similar%20product%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Kashmiri%20saffron%E2%80%99%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saffron%20grown%20in%20the%20Valley%20is%20of%20three%20types%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Lachha%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20variety%20where%20stigmas%20just%20separated%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329424%2Fludhiana-woman-grows-200-plants-in-terrace-garden-watch-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20flowers%20are%20dried%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20further%20processing%3B%20%E2%80%98Mongra%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20variety%20where%20stigmas%20are%20detached%20from%20the%20flower%2C%20dried%20in%20the%20sun%2C%20and%20processed%20traditionally%3B%20and%20%E2%80%98Guchhi%20Saffron%E2%80%99%20which%20also%20does%20not%20involve%20the%20stigmas%20being%20processed.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20dried%20and%20joined%20in%20a%20bundle%20tied%20with%20a%20cloth%20thread.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20that%20the%20Patels%20are%20growing%20is%20the%20second%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20first%20harvest%20was%20an%20experiment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaibhav%20emphasises.%20But%20lucrative%20all%20the%20same.%20Each%20gram%20of%20the%20red%20threads%20fetched%20the%20couple%20Rs%20700.%20As%20for%20the%20road%20ahead%2C%20they%20are%20confident%20they%20can%20expand%20sales%20implementing%20the%20learnings%20of%20the%20previous%20harvest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707485452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG_0318_11zon-1707478888.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D341322%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20to%20grow%20saffron%20at%20home%3F%20Vaibhav%20Patel%20and%20Aastha%20Maheshwari%20Patel%20have%20transformed%20their%20Vadodara%20home%20into%20a%20Kashmiri%20saffron%20haven%2C%20defying%20geographical%20norms.%20They%20share%20insights%20into%20the%20intricate%20process%20of%20growing%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20expensive%20spice%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Woman%E2%80%99s%20Fight%20for%20Equality%20Led%20to%20the%20IAF%20Giving%20Permanent%20Commission%20to%20Female%20Officers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Garima%20Sachdeva%20would%20see%20her%20father%20%E2%80%93%20a%20senior%20rank%20Air%20Force%20officer%20%E2%80%93%20dressed%20up%20in%20the%20blue%20uniform%20every%20morning%2C%20proudly%20placing%20a%20hat%20on%20his%20head.%20He%20would%20wear%20his%20overalls%20and%20flying%20boots%2C%20marching%20to%20his%20workplace%20to%20safeguard%20the%20country%20from%20all%20aerial%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20did%20not%20know%20as%20a%20child%20that%20there%20were%20women%20in%20the%20same%20blue%20uniform%20doing%20the%20exact%20same%20work%20as%20well.%20Despite%20flying%20the%20mean%20machines%20in%20the%20Indian%20skies%20and%20conducting%20all%20the%20ground%20duties%2C%20they%20were%20still%20not%20getting%20what%20I%20saw%20my%20dad%20get%2C%E2%80%9D%20Garima%2C%20now%2032%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20opportunity%20to%20be%20in%20service%20for%20as%20many%20years%20as%20the%20male%20officers%20and%20retirement%20benefits%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%20were%20out%20of%20reach%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20her%20father%20%E2%80%98retired%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20rank%20of%20Air%20Marshal%20after%20serving%20for%20a%20good%2040%20years%2C%20whereas%20women%20officers%20were%20%E2%80%98released%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20service%20only%20after%2010-14%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnowing%20the%20ropes%20of%20gender%20inequality%20in%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20Garima%2C%20who%20practices%20law%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20decided%20to%20fight%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20along%20with%20a%20large%20team%20of%20lawyers.%20They%20were%20led%20by%20Rekha%20Palli%20%5Bnow%20sitting%20Judge%20of%20Delhi%20High%20Court%5D%2C%20and%20her%20competent%20team%20of%20female%20advocates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20us%2C%20she%20explains%20how%20the%20team%20fought%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295810%2Fgender-equality-at-workplace-accenture-empowers-women-for-leadership%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egender%20equality%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Garima%20%5Bcentre%5D%20fought%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20along%20with%20a%20large%20team%20of%20lawyers.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-1707395759-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341178%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGarima%20%5Bcentre%5D%20fought%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights%20along%20with%20a%20large%20team%20of%20lawyers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20case%20in%20detail%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20late%2090s%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20invited%20applications%20from%20women%20to%20join%20as%20Short%20Service%20Commission%20Officers%20(SSCOs)%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20It%20was%20said%20that%20the%20female%20officers%20would%20initially%20be%20granted%20a%20Short%20Service%20Commission%20(SSC)%20for%20five%20years%20at%20the%20end%20of%20which%2C%20a%20permanent%20commission%20would%20be%20granted%20subject%20to%20vacancies%20and%20suitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurprisingly%2C%20the%20IAF%20considered%20only%20male%20officers%20for%20permanent%20commission%20and%20women%20were%20excluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20principal%20grievance%20of%20the%20women%20SSCOs%20was%20that%20by%20denying%20them%20permanent%20commission%20%E2%80%93%20which%20carries%20with%20it%20certain%20privileges%20of%20rank%20including%20pension%20%E2%80%93%20they%20had%20been%20subjected%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F168731%2Fgender-equality-women-empowerment-jamnalal-bajaj-awards%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egender%20discrimination%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGarima%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20short%20service%20commission%20officer%20will%20only%20be%20given%2010%20years%20in%20service%20and%20an%20extension%20of%20four%20years%20maximum.%20So%2C%20female%20officers%20did%20not%20serve%20beyond%2014%20years%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reach%20the%20age%20of%20retirement.%20Whereas%20a%20permanent%20commission%20officer%20will%20serve%20for%20about%2030-35%20years%2C%20or%20more%20depending%20on%20the%20rank.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20opportunity%20was%20not%20given%20to%20women%20officers.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20been%20as%20good%20as%20men%20in%20uniform%2C%20or%20maybe%20better%2C%20then%20why%20were%20we%20not%20given%20permanent%20commission%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20asks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20principal%20grievance%20of%20the%20women%20officers%20was%20that%20by%20denying%20them%20a%20permanent%20commission%2C%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20gender%20discrimination.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-Sachdeva-5-1707395429-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341176%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20principal%20grievance%20of%20the%20women%20officers%20was%20that%20by%20denying%20them%20a%20permanent%20commission%2C%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20gender%20discrimination.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Kargil%20war%20veteran%20(who%20prefers%20to%20remain%20anonymous)%20who%20joined%20the%20armed%20forces%20in%201996%2C%20says%20she%20was%20%E2%80%98released%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20service%20after%20a%20total%20of%2012%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20her%20experience%20in%20the%20IAF%2C%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20underwent%20the%20exact%20same%20training%20of%20one%20year%20along%20with%20male%20cadets.%20We%20never%20took%20help%20from%20anyone%20in%20doing%20our%20duty%20or%20task%2C%20be%20it%20night%20guard%20patrol%20check%20duty%20or%20any%20other%20professional%20task.%20My%20trainer%20said%20no%20one%20should%20be%20able%20to%20say%20that%20we%20were%20less%20than%20any%20male%20counterpart.%20And%20I%20ensured%20that%20no%20one%20could%20point%20out%20anything%20just%20because%20I%20am%20a%20female.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%20individual%20officers%20are%20good%20but%20female%20officers%20in%20general%20were%20treated%20like%20guinea%20pigs%20%E2%80%93%20experimented%20on%20and%20then%20thrown%20away.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20IAF%20and%20serve%20for%20more%20years%2C%20just%20like%20my%20male%20counterparts%2C%20but%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20allowed%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20raise%20this%20issue%2C%2032%20female%20officers%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20court%20and%20in%202003%2C%20a%20Public%20Interest%20Litigation%20(PIL)%20was%20instituted%20before%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20titled%20%E2%80%98Babita%20Puniya%20for%20the%20grant%20of%20permanent%20commission%20to%20women%20SSC%20Officers%E2%80%99%2C%20highlighting%20the%20gender%20discrimination%20being%20meted%20out%20to%20women%20officers%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAfter%20years%20of%20struggle%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20High%20Court%20stated%20that%20the%20Permanent%20Commission%20shall%20be%20offered%20to%20women%20officers%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20five%20years%2C%20subject%20to%20vacancies%20and%20suitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20judgment%20was%20said%20to%20be%20implemented%20by%20the%20IAF%20for%20only%20those%20officers%20who%20were%20in%20service%20or%20those%20retired%2Freleased%20officers%20who%20were%20not%20in%20service%20as%20on%2012%20March%202010%20but%20had%20filed%20writ%20petitions%20before%20their%20release%20%E2%80%93%20a%20criterion%20that%20did%20not%20match%20with%20the%20appellants%20and%20hence%20they%20were%20left%20out%20from%20the%20reinstatement%20plan%20of%20the%20IAF.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20as%20many%20as%2032%20women%20officers%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20won%20a%2012-year-long%20legal%20battle%20against%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGarima-1707458172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341232%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcap