EThis%20variety%20of%20bamboo%20is%20sturdy%20and%20ideal%20for%20converting%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295373%2Feconiture-turns-plastic-waste-into-sustainable-furniture-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einto%20furniture%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20not%20many%20have%20fully%20harnessed%20the%20material%E2%80%99s%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20plant%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Professor%20Ankit%20Kumar%20Changawala%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CBamboo%20is%20the%20future.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20individuals%20who%20have%20made%20efforts%20to%20utilise%20the%20material%20to%20its%20fullest%20extent%2C%20recently%20obtaining%20a%20patent%20for%20a%20bamboo%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20chair%20is%20sturdy%2C%20strong%2C%20and%20can%20last%20up%20to%2020%20years.%20It%20is%20the%20first%20bamboo%20chair%20to%20be%20patented%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESustainability%20meets%20design%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20Surat%2C%20Ankit%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20design%2C%20but%20he%20lacked%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20pursuing%20a%20diploma%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Fthis-single-mother-broke-some-big-barriers-to-become-indias-1st-woman-engineer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecivil%20engineering%2C%20t%3C%2Fa%3Ehinking%20it%20might%20help%20me%20in%20designing%20things.%20However%2C%20during%20the%20course%2C%20I%20realised%20it%20was%20not%20something%20I%20wanted%20to%20pursue.%20It%20was%20my%20professor%E2%80%99s%20brother%2C%20an%20interior%20designer%2C%20whose%20work%20inspired%20me%20and%20made%20me%20realise%20my%20true%20passion%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ankit.